contains:</span></div>\n<div>\n<div>Hydrosoluble&trade; Coenzyme Q-10 (ubiquinone). . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 100 mg</div>\n</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div><span class=\\"bold\\">For all potencies and sizes:</span></div>\n<div><span class=\\"bold\\">Non-medicinal Ingredients: </span>Gelatin, glycerin, sunflower lecithin, medium</div>\n<div>\n<div>chain triglycerides, sunflower oil, purified water, sorbitan monooleate,</div>\n<div>sorbitol, polysorbate 80, titanium dioxide, annatto seed extract, d-alpha</div>\n<div>tocopheryl acetate.</div>\n<p>Free from wheat, gluten, dairy, eggs, nuts, peanuts, fish, shellfish, yeast, sugar, starch, artificial flavours and preservatives.</p>\n</div>', '<p><span style=\\"font-weight: bold;\\">For all potencies and sizes:</span></p>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Directions for Use:</span> Take 1 softsule&reg; up to 3 times daily.</p>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Warnings:</span> Consult a healthcare practitioner prior to use if you are pregnant, breastfeeding or on blood pressure medications or blood thinners.</p>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Cautions:</span> Do not use if the seal is broken. Keep out of reach of children.</p>\n<p>Store in a cool dry place to preserve freshness.</p>', 'CoQ10 MRB | water soluble CoQ10 | Ubiquinone| mitochondrial disease', 'Bio-enhanced natural CoQ10 in water soluble form, has been formulated to provide Maximum Relative Bioavailability (M.R.B.)', 'CoQ10 M.R.B.', '', '', '', '<p>Sans qu\\''il y ait manifestation d\\''effets secondaires, le CoQ10 peut de fa&ccedil;on naturelle aider &agrave; am&eacute;liorer la sant&eacute; cardiovasculaire, &agrave; prolonger la survie des cellules, &agrave; renforcer le soutien du syst&egrave;me immunitaire et &agrave; prot&eacute;ger le corps des dommages caus&eacute;s par les radicaux libres. Dans sept essais cliniques comparatifs avec placebo et &agrave; double insu, le CoQ10 MRB Q-Gel&reg; (biodisponibilit&eacute; relative maximale) s\\''est montr&eacute; efficace dans le traitement de la myocardiopathie (dilatation et &eacute;largissement du myocarde), de l\\''hypertension (haute pression art&eacute;rielle), de l\\''angine de poitrine, de la procidence de la valvule mitrale et de l\\''arythmie cardiaque. Le Q-Gel&reg; est le seul CoQ10 qui est &agrave; la fois hydrosoluble et liposoluble, et est jusqu\\''&agrave; 3 fois plus BIODISPONIBLE! Par exemple, 30 mg de CoQ10 MRB Q-Gel&reg; sont l\\''&eacute;quivalent de 90 mg d\\''autres suppl&eacute;ments de CoQ10. De grade pharmaceutique, brevet&eacute; et dont les bienfaits &agrave; la sant&eacute; et la biodisponibilit&eacute; ont &eacute;t&eacute; &eacute;prouv&eacute;s en clinique, ce suppl&eacute;ment de CoQ10 est class&eacute; au premier rang &agrave; travers le monde et a gagn&eacute; la confiance des Canadiens. Le CoQ10 MRB est utilis&eacute; au centre hospitalier pour enfants chef de file de l\\''Ontario pour le traitement de la cytopathie mitochondriale.</p>', '', '', '', '', 4, 'No', '', 'CoQ10 MRB 30mg 80018047; CoQ10 MRB 60mg 80012965;  CoQ10 MRB 100mg 80009553', 'Active'),
(2, 'vt10200', 1, 'CoQ10 M.R.B. Liquid Drops', 'Hydrosoluble™ Coenzyme Q-10 (ubiquinone)', 'An antioxidant that supports cardiovascular health.', '<p>While every cell in the body requires Coenzyme Q10 (CoQ10) to produce energy, the cells in the heart require some of the most significant amounts.&nbsp; Clinical studies have shown that CoQ10 can reduce the risk for cardiovascular problems.&nbsp; Since the body converts ubiquinone into ubiquinol, there is an extra  conversion step involved.&nbsp; This conversion process generally declines as  we age, hence &nbsp; ubiquinone is generally used for younger age groups and ubquinol for older age groups.</p>\n<p>Bio-enhanced natural CoQ10 in water soluble form (ubiquinone)&nbsp; has been formulated to provide Maximum Relative Bioavailability (M.R.B.).</p>\n<h5><span class=\\"\\\\&quot;bold\\\\&quot; bold\\">Key Benefits:</span></h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Ideal for people that cannot have difficulties swallowing softgels</li>\n<li>Clinically studied in humans demonstrate efficacy</li>\n<li>3X the absorption when compared with standard CoQ10 supplements</li>\n<li>Utilizes LiQSorb&reg;, a&nbsp;bioavailability enhanced Coenzyme Q10 that in-vitro studies confirm better absorption</li>\n</ul>', '<p>This  year, heart disease will affect more women in Canada than any other  disease.&nbsp; Cardiovascular afflictions can include atherosclerosis, hypertension, stroke and heart attack.&nbsp;</p>\n<h5><span class=\\"bold\\">About&nbsp;<strong>CoQ10 &nbsp;</strong></span></h5>\n<p>Coenzyme Q10 (CoQ10) is an extremely important nutrient that every cell in your body must have in order to produce energy. It is naturally found in the energy-producing center of the cell known as the mitochondria, the part of a cell responsible for the production of energy in the form of ATP (Adenosine triphosphate). ATP serves as the cell\\''s major energy source and drives a number of biological processes, including muscle contraction and the production of protein. CoQ10 is involved in making this important molecule.</p>\n<h5><span class=\\"bold\\">About&nbsp;</span><strong><span class=\\"bold\\">CoQ10 M.R.B</span>.</strong></h5>\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong>CoQ10 MRB utilizes&nbsp;LiQSorb&reg;, a&nbsp;bioavailability enhanced Coenzyme Q10&nbsp;that in-vitro studies confirm 300% better absorption (vs standard CoQ10) and cell culture studies confirm enhanced intestinal permeability.&nbsp;Innovite Health CoQ10 M.R.B is currently used &nbsp;at a leading&nbsp; Ontario &nbsp;children\\''s hospital to treat Mitochondiral Cytopathies.</p>\n<p>Also shown effectiveness in the treatment of:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Cardiomyopathy (dilated and enlarged heart muscle)</li>\n<li>Hypertension (high blood pressure)</li>\n<li>Angina (heart pain),</li>\n<li>Mitral valve prolapsed</li>\n<li>Arrhythmia.</li>\n</ul>\n<h5>Sources:</h5>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3459498/\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Hans M, Prakash S, Gupta S. Clinical evaluation of topical application of perio-Q gel (Coenzyme Q(10)) in chronic periodontitis patients. J Indian Soc Periodontol. 2012 Apr;16(2):193-9.</a></li>\n<li><a href=\\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/16873952\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Gvozdj&aacute;kov&aacute; A, et al. Coenzyme Q10 supplementation reduces corticosteroids dosage in patients with bronchial asthma. Biofactors. 2005;25(1-4):235-40.</a></li>\n<li><a href=\\"http://www.internationaljournalofcardiology.com/article/S0167-5273(98)00323-4/abstract\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Singh RB, Niaz MA. Serum concentration of lipoprotein(a) decreases on treatment with hydrosoluble coenzyme Q10 in patients with coronary artery disease: discovery of a new role. Int J Cardiol. 1999 Jan;68(1):23-9</a></li>\n<li><a href=\\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9565826\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Chopra RK, et al. Relative bioavailability of coenzyme Q10 formulations in human subjects. Int J Vitam Nutr Res. 1998;68(2):109-13.</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>For over 30 years, Innovite Health has been inspiring wellness. When the body&rsquo;s core systems work in synergy, optimal health can be achieved. Our goal to nourish and heal the body from the inside out: restoring nutrients and repairing damage so you can reclaim your health. Our nutritional foundation is built from the latest research and clinical evidence. Safe, natural and effective &ndash; Innovite Health for your body&rsquo;s needs, at every stage of life.</p>', '<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Ingredients:</span> Each 1 ml contains:<br /> HydrosolubleTM CoQ10 (ubiquinone) -100 mg</p>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Non Medicinal Ingredients:</span> Purified water, medium chain triglycerides, soy lecithin, polysorbate 80, citric acid, potassium sorbate and alpha tocopherol.</p>', '<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Directions for Use</span> (Adult Dosage): Take 1 ml 1-3 times daily in water or any beverage.</p>', 'CoQ10 MRB Liquid | water soluble CoQ10 | Ubiquinone| mitochondrial disease', 'Bio-enhanced natural CoQ10 in water soluble form, has been formulated to provide Maximum Relative Bioavailability (M.R.B.)', 'CoQ10 M.R.B. Gouttes liquides', '', '', '', '<p>Les gouttes LiQsorbTM CoQ10 sont formul&eacute;es en utilisant la technologie Li-Q-sorb, un complexe r&eacute;volutionnaire de CoQ10 qui est 300% plus biodisponnible et qui permet une absorption am&eacute;lior&eacute;e.</p>', '', '', '', '', 4, 'No', '', '80007078', 'Active'),
(3, 'vt-01-01', 1, 'Formula H.H.', '30+ synergistic cardiovascular ingredients', 'Promotes heart health and arterial cleansing', '<p>Formula H.H. is a broad spectrum high potency multi-vitamin/mineral formula that focuses on the overall cardiovascular system.&nbsp;</p>\n<h5><span class=\\"bold\\">Key Benefits:</span></h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Over 30 ingredients acting synergistically for an arterial cleansing effect</li>\n<li>Promotes healthy cardiovascular circulation&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Helps inhibit arterial plaque formation and may reverse existing&nbsp;plaque</li>\n</ul>', '<p>The blood carries nutrients and oxygen to every cell in the body, and carries away waste<br />materials from those same cells for excretion. The unimpeded flow of blood<br />throughout the whole body is critical for every body function and for keeping energy levels high.<br />Atherosclerosis begins when something injures the inner lining of an artery.<br />Many physicians now believe that the initial damage may be caused by free radical molecules<br />created from exposure to environmental pollution, poor quality food, cigarette smoke and high<br />levels of stress. As with any injury, the body attempts to repair the wound in the artery lining. In<br />the process, a destructive chain reaction can be set into motion, which results in thickening of<br />the arterial wall; this thickening, in turn, obstructs the artery. Arterial obstructions are called<br />plaques or atheromas. As the plaque grows inside an artery, blood flow is reduced, with<br />potentially very serious health consequences. Clearing arterial plaques can improve circulation<br />and quality of life while reducing the risk of serious and debilitating cardiovascular illnesses.</p>\n<h5>Formula HH ingredients benefits include:</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>High Potency Antioxidant Vitamins C, E, A, B,</li>\n<li>Folic Acid for homocysteine reduction</li>\n<li>Vitamin D required for optimal cardiovascular health</li>\n<li>Magnesium normalizes blood pressure and prevents arrhythmias</li>\n<li>Potassium Supports healthy muscle contraction, transmitting electrochemical impulses and maintaining blood pressure</li>\n<li>Chromium helps maintain stable blood sugar levels</li>\n<li>Selenium protects lipids from oxidation</li>\n<li>Betaine hydrochloride helps with nutrient break-down and absorption</li>\n<li>Chollne emulsifies and reduces stickiness fat</li>\n<li>Cysteine is a chelating agent and free radical scavenger</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>For over 30 years, Innovite Health has been inspiring wellness. When the body&rsquo;s core systems work in synergy, optimal health can be achieved. Our goal to nourish and heal the body from the inside out: restoring nutrients and repairing damage so you can reclaim your health. Our nutritional foundation is built from the latest research and clinical evidence. Safe, natural and effective &ndash; Innovite Health for your body&rsquo;s needs, at every stage of life.</p>', '<div>\n<div><span class=\\"bold\\">Medicinal Ingredients:</span></div>\n<div>Each tablet contains:</div>\n<div>Vitamin A(palmitate).........1200 mcg RAE (4000 IU)</div>\n<div>Vitamin D3(cholecalciferol)............1.625 mcg (65 IU)</div>\n<div>Vitamin E (d-alpha tocopherylacetate)......................43.5 mg AT (65 IU)</div>\n<div>Vitamin C (ascorbic acid).................. 300 mg</div>\n<div>Vitamin C(calcium ascorbate)...................... 100 mg</div>\n<div>Vitamin B1(thiamine hydrochloride)................ 20 mg</div>\n<div>Vitamin B2 (riboflavin) .......................... 5 mg</div>\n<div>Vitamin B6(pyridoxine hydrochloride)..............15 mg</div>\n<div>Vitamin B12 (cyanocobalamin)..........25 mcg</div>\n<div>Niacinamide.......................................... 5 mg</div>\n<div>Niacin.................................................... 5 mg</div>\n<div>Pantothenic Acid(calcium d-pantothenate)............... 50 mg</div>\n<div>Folic Acid .........................................0.04 mg</div>\n<div>Biotin................................................. 10 mcg</div>\n<div>Choline Bitartrate.................................70 mg</div>\n<div>Inositol ..................................................5 mg</div>\n<div>dl-Methionine.......................................25 mg</div>\n<div>Magnesium (oxide)..............................40 mg</div>\n<div>Potassium (chloride, citrate)................40 mg</div>\n<div>Manganese (gluconate)......................0.5 mg</div>\n<div>Zinc (gluconate).....................................3 mg</div>\n<div>Chromium (HVP chelate) ................. 20 mcg</div>\n<div>Selenium (HVP chelate) ................... 25 mcg</div>\n<div>Iodine (potassium iodide) ..............0.025 mg</div>\n<div>Calcium (carbonate) ...........................40 mg</div>\n<div>Betaine Hydrochloride ........................24 mg</div>\n<div>l-Cysteine Hydrochloride ...................100 mg</div>\n<div>Thymus concentrate............................10 mg</div>\n<div>Spleen concentrate..............................10 mg</div>\n<div>Adrenal concentrate ............................10 mg</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><span class=\\"bold\\">Non-medicinal Ingredients:</span></div>\n<div>Microcrystalline cellulose, hydroxypropyl</div>\n<div>methylcellulose, colloidal silicon dioxide,</div>\n<div>magnesium stearate, purified water,</div>\n<div>carnauba wax, natural vanilla flavour.</div>\n<p>Free from sugar, starch, dairy, wheat,</p>\n<p>gluten, corn, eggs, soy, yeast, fish,</p>\n<p>shellfish, nuts, peanuts, artificial colours,</p>\n<p>flavours and preservatives.</p>\n</div>', '<div><span class=\\"bold\\">Direction for Use:</span> (Adults): Take 2 tablets daily.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><span class=\\"bold\\">Cautions:</span> For therapeutic use only. Consult with a healthcare practitioner prior to</div>\n<div>\n<div>use. Do not use if the seal is broken. Keep out of reach of children. Store in a</div>\n<div>cool, dry place to preserve freshness.</div>\n</div>', 'Formula HH | 30+ syngergistic ingredients for heart health ', 'Formula H.H. is a broad spectrum high potency multi-vitamin/mineral formula that focuses on the overall cardiovascular system.', 'Formule H.H.', '', '', '', '<p>La Formule H.H. est une formule de multivitamines et min&eacute;raux &agrave; large spectre et &agrave; puissance &eacute;lev&eacute;e, compos&eacute;e de 30 nutriments qui pourraient avoir des effets b&eacute;n&eacute;fiques sur le syst&egrave;me cardiovasculaire. Fabriqu&eacute;e au Canada, la Formule H.H. contient de la b&eacute;ta&iuml;ne pour un soutien digestif. Cette formule est un suppl&eacute;ment nutritionnel global unique et excellent.</p>', '', '', '', '', 5, 'No', '', '02241346(DIN)', 'Active'),
(4, 'vt-01-21', 1, 'Magnesium Citrate', '', 'Helps in the maintenance of proper muscle function and tissue formation; in the development and maintenance of bones and teeth; also assists the body to metabolize carbohydrates, fats and proteins.', '<p>\n<p>Magnesium Citrate quickly restores the magnesium levels in the body to healthy levels which leads to an improvement in heart function and prevention of cardiovascular disease.&nbsp; Magnesium Citrate alone or in combination with other Innovite Cardiovascular Health products will allow you to reclaim your health and continue enjoying your life to the fullest.</p>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Key Benefits:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Crucial to a well functioning cardiovascular system</li>\n<li>Clinically proven to reduce the incidence of high blood pressure</li>\n<li>Maintains the normal electrical activity of the heart</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</p>', '<p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;\\">Magnesium is an essential mineral in human nutrition with a wide range of biological functions. Magnesium is involved in over 300 metabolic reactions. It is necessary for every major biological process, including the production of cellular energy and the synthesis of nucleic acids and proteins. Magnesium is also important for maintaining the normal electrical activity of the heart.</p>\n</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\"><em style=\\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 8.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\\">For over 30 years, Innovite Health has been inspiring wellness. When the body&rsquo;s core systems work in synergy, optimal health can be achieved. Our goal to nourish and heal the body from the inside out: restoring nutrients and repairing damage so you can reclaim your health. Our nutritional foundation is built from the latest research and clinical evidence. Safe, natural and effective &ndash; Innovite Health for your body&rsquo;s needs, at every stage of life.</span></em></p>\n</p>', '<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><span class=\\"bold\\">Medicinal Ingredients</span>: Each capsule contains:</div>\n<div>\n<div>Magnesium (citrate, oxide)&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.250 mg</div>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<div><span class=\\"bold\\">Non-medicinal Ingredients:</span> Malic acid (280 mg), microcrystalline</div>\n<div>\n<div>cellulose, silicon dioxide, magnesium stearate and gelatin.</div>\n&nbsp; &nbsp;</div>\n<div>Free from yeast,</div>\n<div>\n<div>sugar, wheat, gluten,</div>\n<div>corn, dairy, eggs,</div>\n<div>soy, GMO, artificial</div>\n<div>colours, flavours and</div>\n<div>preservatives.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span class=\\"bold\\">QUALITY, PURITY AND&nbsp;POTENCY GUARANTEED.</span></div>\n</div>', '<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Directions for Use:</span> Adults: Take 1 capsule once or twice daily with food,</p>\n<p>or as directed by a healthcare practitioner.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Cautions:</span> Some people may experience diarrhoea. Do not use if the seal</p>\n<p>is broken. Keep out of reach of children. Store in a cool dry place to</p>\n<p>preserve freshness.</p>', '', '', 'Citrate de magnésium', '', '', '', '<p>Le magn&eacute;sium est un min&eacute;ral essentiel &agrave; la nutrition humaine, qui comporte une panoplie de fonctions biologiques. Le magn&eacute;sium participe &agrave; plus de 300 r&eacute;actions m&eacute;taboliques. C\\''est un min&eacute;ral essentiel dans chaque processus biologique majeur, dont la production de l\\''&eacute;nergie cellulaire et la synth&egrave;se des acides nucl&eacute;iques et des prot&eacute;ines. Le citrate de magn&eacute;sium est vital au bon fonctionnement du syst&egrave;me cardiovasculaire. Des &eacute;tudes ont d&eacute;montr&eacute; que les personnes qui prennent un suppl