(8, 'ad-27-03', 2, 'Yeast Buster™ Psyllium Powder', 'Husks and seeds', 'Bulk forming fibre laxative that promotes bowel movements by increasing bulk volume and water content.', '<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\">Yeast Buster Psyllium Powder is one of the 4 pillars of the Yeast Buster<span class=\\"tx-largebold\\">&trade;</span> Kit. This finely ground powder uses the highest quality Psyllium seed husks which are portions of the seeds of the Plantago ovate plant. Psyllum Powder is a source of soluble dietary fiber and is used as part of the Yeast Buster Kit for maximum intestinal cleansing effect.</p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\"><strong>Key Benefits:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Forces the Caproil and Bentonite against the sides of the colon</li>\n<li>Softens hardened fecal matter for easier elimination</li>\n<li>Absorptive ability complements Bentonite&rsquo;s toxin-attracting properties</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\">Psyllium Powder can be used alone but is most effective when is used as part of the Yeast Buster&rsquo;s Kit</p>', '<p>This finely ground powder uses the highest quality Psyllium husks and seeds, for maximum intestinal cleansing effect. The bulking and lubricating husk softens hardened fecal matter for easier elimination, while the grainy seed powder acts as a gentle \\"scr</p>', '<p>Medicinal Ingredients: Each rounded teaspoon (7 g) contains:</p>\n<p>Psyllium (Plantago ovata) husk powder&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;3.5 g</p>\n<p>Psyllium (Plantago ovata) seed powder&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;3.5 g</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>QUALITY, PURITY AND POTENCY GUARANTEED.</p>\n<p>Free from soy, yeast, sugar, starch, wheat, corn, dairy,</p>\n<p>eggs, nuts, peanuts, fish, shellfish, GMO, artificial</p>\n<p>colours, flavours and preservatives.</p>', '<p>Directions for Use: Adults: Add 1 rounded tsp (7 g) into 8 oz of liquid, once daily. Mix well and drink</p>\n<p>immediately. Take on an empty stomach (1/2 hour before meals or 2 hours after; and 2 hours before or after</p>\n<p>taking other medications). Effects observed 12-24 hours after first dose, and may take 2-3 days.</p>\n<p>Important: In addition, drink 6-8 glasses of water each day.</p>\n<p>For Candida-related conditions, use in conjuction with Innovite Health&rsquo;s Yeast Buster&reg; Candida Trauma Kit.</p>\n<p>Cautions: Consult a healthcare practitioner if symptoms worsen or if laxative effect does not occur within seven</p>\n<p>days; if you experience chest pain, vomiting, or difficulty in swallowing or breathing after taking this product.</p>\n<p>Consult a healthcare practitioner prior to use if you have symptoms such as abdominal pain, nausea, vomiting</p>\n<p>or fever and/or if you are taking medications which inhibit peristaltic movement (e.g. opioids, loperamide).</p>\n<p>Contraindications: Do not use if you have difficulty swallowing; if you have diabetes mellitus in which blood</p>\n<p>sugar is difficult to regulate; if you are experiencing a sudden change in bowel habits that has persisted for more</p>\n<p>than 2 weeks, undiagnosed rectal bleeding, or failure to defecate following the use of another laxative product.</p>\n<p>Known Adverse Reactions: Hypersensitivity, such as allergy, has been known to occur following inhaled</p>\n<p>and/or ingested psyllium; in which case, discontinue use. May cause temporary gas and/or bloating.</p>\n<p>Do not use if the seal is broken. Keep out of reach of children. Store in a cool dry place to preserve freshness.</p>', '', '', 'Psyllium de Yeast Buster', '', '', '', '<p>Cette poudre finement moulue utilise les cosses et les graines de psyllium de la meilleure qualit&eacute; qui soit, pour un nettoyage intestinal d\\''une efficacit&eacute; maximale. L\\''effet lubrifiant et volumisant des cosses ramollit les mati&egrave;res f&eacute;cales endurcies pour une &eacute;limination plus facile, alors que la poudre de graines de psyllium de texture granuleuse agit en douceur comme une \\"brosse &agrave; r&eacute;curer\\".</p>', '', '', '', '', 5, 'No', '', '80011770', 'Active'),
(9, 'vt-27-15', 2, 'Yeast Buster™  DDS Acidophilus', '', 'Contributes to a natural healthy gut flora.', '<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\">Yeast Buster DDS Acidophilus is one of the Four Pillars of the Yeast Buster Kit. This unique probiotic has been formulated with 5 billion colony forming units of DDS Lactobacillus acidophilus to help replenish the gut with healthy bacteria.</p>\n<p style=\\"font-size: 10px;\\"><span class=\\"bold\\">Key Benefits:</span></p>\n<ul style=\\"font-size: 10px;\\">\n<li>Utilizes Lactobacillus acidophilus (DDS-1&reg; strain)</li>\n<li>Contains 5 billion colony forming units (CFU) per serving</li>\n<li>Promotes overall digestive health and regular bowel movements</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 10px;\\">Restores the intestinal population of friendly bacteria</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 10px;\\">Inclusion of DDS Acidophilus in the anti-Candida regime is a vital step towards warding off pathogenic organisms</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 10px;\\">Ensures long term balance of healthy bacteria affected by Candidaiasis</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class=\\"tx-capshead\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-CA; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\\"><br style=\\"mso-special-character: line-break; page-break-before: always;\\" /> </span></span></p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\"><span class=\\"tx-capshead\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-CA;\\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>', '<p><span class=\\"bold\\">DDS Probiotic Family Overview:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Superior robust strain: Survives stomach acid and bile for a healthy intestinal flora; human origin for easy adaptability.&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Clinically researched proprietary formulas: Clinically proven in double blind placebo human trials.&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Fortified with prebiotics:&nbsp; Feeds, nourishes and increases probiotic bacteria.</li>\n<li>Complete family care: Full line from infant to urgent care.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Restore the healthy balance of intestinal flora</span></p>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Repair the gut ecosystem disrupted by a disturbance (i.e. infection, antibiotic induced diarrhea, etc.)</span></p>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Reclaim a healthy gut.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">&nbsp;Sources:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\\"http://www.cabdirect.org/abstracts/19800465097.html;jsessionid=46EAA31964AC7726A6DB839218835E16\\" target=\\"_blank\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: &quot;HelveticaNeueLTStd-Lt&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: HelveticaNeueLTStd-Lt;\\">Ayebo, A. D., I. A. Angelo, and K. M. Shahani. 1980. Effect of ingesting&nbsp;</span><em><span style=\\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: &quot;HelveticaNeueLTStd-LtIt&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: HelveticaNeueLTStd-LtIt;\\">Lactobacillus acidophilus</span></em></a><span style=\\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: HelveticaNeueLTStd-Lt, sans-serif;\\"><a href=\\"http://www.cabdirect.org/abstracts/19800465097.html;jsessionid=46EAA31964AC7726A6DB839218835E16\\" target=\\"_blank\\">milk upon fecal flora and enzyme activity in human. Milchwissenschaft, 35: 730-733</a>.</span></li>\n<li><a style=\\"font-family: HelveticaNeueLTStd-Lt, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\\" href=\\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/2064229\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Gerasimov S. V. et al. 2013. Role of probiotics in attenuation of acute respiratory tract infections in preschool</a>&nbsp;<a style=\\"font-family: HelveticaNeueLTStd-Lt, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\\" href=\\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/2064229\\" target=\\"_blank\\">and primary school children. In press.</a></li>\n<li><a style=\\"font-family: HelveticaNeueLTStd-Lt, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\\" href=\\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/20642296\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Gerasimov S. V., Vasjuta V. V., Myhovych O. O., Bondarchuk L. I. 2010. Probiotic supplement reduces atopic dermatits in preschool children. Am J Clin Dermatol, 11:351-361</a><span style=\\"font-family: HelveticaNeueLTStd-Lt, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\\">.</span></li>\n<li><a style=\\"font-family: HelveticaNeueLTStd-Lt, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\\" href=\\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/14968899\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Gerasimov S. V. 2004. Probiotic prophylaxis in pediatric recurrent urinary tract infections. Clin Pediatr., 43:95-98.</a></li>\n<li><a style=\\"font-family: HelveticaNeueLTStd-Lt, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\\" href=\\"http://www.probioticsincanada.com/en/pdfs/IBS%20Study-%20Published%20Article.pdf\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Nagala R., Routray C. 2011. Clinical Case Study&mdash;Multispecies probiotic supplement minimizes symptoms of irritable bowel syndrome. US Gastroenterol Hepatol., 7: 36-37.</a></li>\n</ul>', '<p>DDS Original Capsules</p>\n<p>Medicinal Ingredients:</p>\n<p>Each 500 mg capsule is guaranteed to contain a minimum of 2.5 billion colony</p>\n<p>forming units (CFU) of Lactobacillus acidophilus (DDS-1&reg; strain) at the expiry date.</p>\n<p>Non Medicinal Ingredients:</p>\n<p>Rice maltodextrin, Magnesium stearate, Vegetable cellulose and FOS</p>\n<p>(Fructooligosaccharides)</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>DDS Original Powder</p>\n<p>Medicinal Ingredients:</p>\n<p>Each gram (1/4 teaspoon) is guaranteed to contain a minimum of 5 billion colony</p>\n<p>forming units (CFU) of Lactobacillus acidophilus (DDS-1&reg; strain) at the expiry date.</p>\n<p>Non Medicinal Ingredients:</p>\n<p>Rice maltodextrin, Magnesium stearate and FOS (Fructooligosaccharides)</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>DDS&reg; is a registered trademark of UAS Laboratories, Inc.</p>', '<p>DDS Original Capsules</p>\n<p>Directions for Use: Recommended Adult Dose: Take 2 capsules daily on an</p>\n<p>empty stomach, or as recommended by your healthcare practitioner.</p>\n<p>Cautions: Sealed for your protection. Do not use if the seal is broken. Keep out</p>\n<p>of reach of children. Keep refrigerated once opened. Do not freeze. Discontinue</p>\n<p>use and consult a health care practitioner if symptoms of digestive upset (e.g.</p>\n<p>diarrhea) occur, worsen, or persist beyond 3 days.</p>\n<p>Contraindications: Do not use if you are experiencing nausea, fever, vomiting,</p>\n<p>bloody diarrhea or severe abdominal pain. Do not use if you have an</p>\n<p>immune-compromised condition.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>DDS Original Powder</p>\n<p>Directions for Use: Recommended Adult Dose: Take &frac14; teaspoon (1 g) powder</p>\n<p>daily in water on an empty stomach or as recommended by your healthcare</p>\n<p>practitioner. Due to its potential to clump in water, best if taken directly into the</p>\n<p>mouth, or added to a drink using a blender or shaker cup.</p>\n<p>Cautions: Sealed for your protection. Do not use if the seal is broken. Keep out</p>\n<p>of reach of children. Keep refrigerated once opened. Do not freeze. Discontinue</p>\n<p>use and consult a health care practitioner if symptoms of digestive upset (e.g.</p>\n<p>diarrhea) occur, worsen, or persist beyond 3 days.</p>\n<p>Contraindications: Do not use if you are experiencing nausea, fever, vomiting,</p>\n<p>bloody diarrhea or severe abdominal pain. Do not use if you have an</p>\n<p>immune-compromised condition.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>QUALITY, PURITY AND POTENCY GUARANTEED.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Free from dairy, corn, wheat, gluten, soy, nuts, peanuts, eggs, fish, shellfish,</p>\n<p>yeast, GMO, artificial colours, flavours or preservatives.</p>', '', '', 'DDS Acidophilus de Yeast Buster', '', '', '', '<p>Afin d\\''aider &agrave; repeupler la flore intestinale de bact&eacute;ries saines, la trousse Yeast Buster inclut le produit DDS Acidophilus. La plupart des programmes anti-candidose n\\''incluent pas de bonnes bact&eacute;ries sous la forme d\\''acidophilus, qui est une &eacute;tape vitale dans la lutte contre les organismes pathog&egrave;nes comme le candida. Les probiotiques DDS d\\''Inno-Vite sont BREVET&Eacute;S, &Eacute;PROUV&Eacute;S, CONTIENNENT LA PLUS GRANDE QUANTIT&Eacute; DE BACT&Eacute;RIES PAR GRAME, SONT EXEMPTS D\\''INGR&Eacute;DIENTS LAITIERS et sont d\\''une SOUCHE SUPERIEURE. Aujourd\\''hui, tous les produits DDS contiennent des FOS (fructooligosaccharideS) qui, sans aucun risque, renforcent la prolif&eacute;ration de bact&eacute;ries b&eacute;n&eacute;fiques dans les intestins. Offert s&eacute;par&eacute;ment ou dans la trousse Yeast Buster.</p>', '', '', '', '', 3, 'No', '', '80011360', 'Active'),
(10, 'ad-27-08', 2, 'Yeast Buster™  Olive Leaf Extract', '', 'Supports immune function', '<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 8.0pt; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\\">The Olive Leaf has been used for centuries by Middle Eastern cultures as a powerful natural antibacterial to treat fevers and a broad spectrum of microbial disorders as it is lethal to fungus and many undesirable bacteria. It is the pungent components found in the leaves or polyphenols that are especially effective in preventing damage caused by bacteria.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 8.0pt; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\\"><span class=\\"bold\\">Key Benefits:</span></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Combats fungus beyond the colon (already being protected by the Yeast Buster Candida Trauma Kit)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Formulation includes contains 12% Oleuropein and additional synergistic whole herb powder to ensure optimum assimilation and effectiveness</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Standardized Olive Leaf Extract amplifies the effectiveness of the Yeast Buster Candida Trauma Kit</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Non toxic approach to immune strengthening</span></li>\n</ul>', '<p>The active ingredient in Olive Leaf Extract is called Oleuropein, and it has</p>\n<p>powerful healing properties that fight the bacteria, viruses, fungi and</p>\n<p>parasites that cause infection and disease. The anti-viral activity of Olive Leaf</p>\n<p>Extract is due to the action of Oleuropein on the protein coat of the virus. It</p>\n<p>is thought to inactivate micro-organisms by dissolving the outer lining of the</p>\n<p>microbe and is able to penetrate infected cells. The synergistic structure of</p>\n<p>anti-oxidant polyphenols, esters, flavonoids, and multiple iridoids work</p>\n<p>together to weaken disease causing organisms and interfere with the ability</p>\n<p>of a virus to assemble at the cell membrane.</p>\n<p>Olive Leaf Extract also helps to build the immune system by stimulating</p>\n<p>phagocyte production which enables immune cells to destroy infectious</p>\n<p>organisms. Olive Leaf Extract acts to prevent the onset of colds, flu, and a</p>\n<p>range of viruses, yeast, fungal and mould problems, bacterial infections and</p>\n<p>parasites. It has even been found as an effective and preventive treatment</p>\n<p>for malaria.</p>\n<p>Innovite Health&rsquo;s standardized Olive Leaf Extract amplifies the effectiveness</p>\n<p>of the Innovite Health&rsquo;s Yeast Buster Candida Trauma Kit. Where the</p>\n<p>Candidiasis is systemic, Olive Leaf Extract can combat fungus beyond the</p>\n<p>colon.</p>\n<p>Each vegetarian capsule of Innovite Health\\''s Olive Leaf Extract contains 250 mg</p>\n<p>of standardized olive leaf extract (12% oleuropein) combined with additional</p>\n<p>synergy of 250 mg of whole herb powder to ensure optimum assimilation</p>\n<p>and effectiveness.</p>', '<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Medicinal Ingredients: </span>Each vegetarian capsule contains:</p>\n<p>Olive Leaf (Olea europaea) Extract-12% oleuropein&hellip;&hellip;...&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.......................250 mg</p>\n<p>Olive Leaf (Olea europaea) Powder&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;....................250 mg</p>\n<p>Zinc (citrate)&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;....................0.35 mg</p>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Non-medicinal Ingredients:</span> Microcrystalline cellulose, magnesium stearate (vegetarian),</p>\n<p>hydroxypropyl methylcellulose (vegetarian capsule).</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>QUALITY, PURITY AND POTENCY GUARANTEED.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Free from soy, yeast, sugar,</p>\n<p>starch, wheat, gluten, corn,</p>\n<p>dairy, eggs, nuts, peanuts, fish,</p>\n<p>shellfish, GMO, artificial</p>\n<p>colours, flavours or</p>\n<p>preservatives.</p>', '<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Directions for Use:</span> (Adults) : Take 2 capsules once daily with food. Take a few hours</p>\n<p>before or after taking other medications.</p>\n<p>Warnings: Consult a healthcare practitioner prior to use if you are pregnant or</p>\n<p>breastfeeding.</p>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Cautions:</span> Do not use if the seal is broken. Keep out of reach of children. Store in a cool</p>\n<p>dry place to preserve freshness. For Candida-related conditions use in conjunction with Innovite Health&rsquo;s Yeast Buster&reg; Trauma kit.</p>', '', '', 'Extrait de feuille d\\''olivier Yeast Buster', '', '', '', '<p>L\\''Extrait normalis&eacute; de feuille d\\''olivier (tel que pr&eacute;sent&eacute; dans le Guide Yeast Buster &agrave; la rescousse) amplifie l\\''efficacit&eacute; de la trousse anti-candidose Yeast Buster. L&agrave; o&ugrave; la candidose est syst&eacute;mique, l\\''Extrait de feuille d\\''olivier peut lutter contre les champignons au-del&agrave; du c&ocirc;lon. La feuille d\\''olivier est utilis&eacute;e depuis des si&egrave;cles dans les cultures du Moyen-Orient pour traiter la fi&egrave;vre et un large spectre de troubles microbiens, car elle est mortelle pour les champignons et de nombreuses bact&eacute;ries  ind&eacute;sirables. L\\''Extrait de feuille d\\''olivier Yeast Buster contient 12% d\\''oleurop&eacute;ine qui est combin&eacute;e &agrave; la synergie additionnelle de la poudre de plante enti&egrave;re afin d\\''assurer une assimilation et une efficacit&eacute; maximales.</p>', '', '', '', '', 10, 'No', '', '80027062', 'Active'),
