yle-rowband-size:0; 	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0; 	mso-style-noshow:yes; 	mso-style-priority:99; 	mso-style-parent:\\"\\"; 	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; 	mso-para-margin-top:0cm; 	mso-para-margin-right:0cm; 	mso-para-margin-bottom:10.0pt; 	mso-para-margin-left:0cm; 	line-height:115%; 	mso-pagination:widow-orphan; 	font-size:11.0pt; 	font-family:\\"Calibri\\",\\"sans-serif\\"; 	mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri; 	mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; 	mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; 	mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin; 	mso-fareast-language:EN-US;} --> <!--[endif] --></p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\"><span style=\\"mso-fareast-language: EN-CA;\\">Grapefruit Seed Extract is a broad spectrum anti-microbial, available in two formats: Liquid drops and vegetarian tablets. Both products are tested to be free from benzethonium chloride and benzalkonium chloride<br />(toxic pesticides typically found in lesser-quality grapefruit seed extracts).</span></p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\"><strong style=\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\\"><span style=\\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-language: EN-CA;\\">Key Benefits:</span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Clears the body of harmful bacteria, viruses, infection and fungi, simultaneously promoting and protecting the immune system. Also assists the body with elimination of some parasites</li>\n<li>Easily tolerated, extremely potent, and doesn\\''t affect beneficial bacteria</li>\n<li>Promotes a more alkaline environment in the body which allows for the metabolic, enzymatic, immunologic, and repair mechanisms function at their best</li>\n<li>Powerful antibacterial, antifungal and antimicrobial effects are useful in fighting a large range of infections, parasites and viruses</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\"><span style=\\"mso-fareast-language: EN-CA;\\"><span style=\\"mso-spacerun: yes;\\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>', '<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\"><span style=\\"mso-fareast-language: EN-CA;\\">Grapefruit seed extract</span> is an antibacterial and antifungal nutrient that helps relieve symptoms<br />of  upper respiratory tract including colds, flu, and strep throat, and  gastrointestinal tract disorders including flatulence and diarrhoea, and  candidiasis.</p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\"><span style=\\"mso-fareast-language: EN-CA;\\">Grapefruit  seed extract is made from the seeds of organically grown grapefruits  and oregano. It is a powerful broad spectrum antimicrobial and  antifungal nutrient that is widely recommended for its germ-killing  capabilities, relief of gastric discomfort and for relief of  Candidia-related symptoms.&nbsp; </span><span style=\\"font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-language: EN-CA;\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\">Grapefruit seed extract is a powerful antimicrobial used for its antibacterial,<br />antiseptic and purifying properties. It clears the body of harmful bacteria,<br />viruses, infection and fungi, simultaneously promoting and protecting the<br />immune system. It has the ability to rid the body of some parasites as well.<br />Grapefruit seed extract has an alkalizing effect on the body and is considered<br />one of the strongest foods for promoting alkaline in the body. For optimum<br />health, alkaline and acid levels must be balanced in the body, which is<br />referred as the pH level. Excess acids create oxidation, effectively causing<br />the body decay and become sick.</p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\">Although it is not a component of the Yeast Buster Kit, it can be added to the Candida regime to further boost its effects.</p>', '<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Grapefruit Seed Extract 50mL</span></p>\n<p>Medicinal Ingredients: Each drop (0.05 mL) contains:<br />Bioflavonoids (from certified organic grapefruit (Citrus paradisi) seed<br />extract)&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;......0.4 mg<br />Oregano (Origanum vulgare) leaf extract ([1:10] equivalent to 0.03 mg)...3 mcg<br />Vitamin C (ascorbic acid)&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;............................................1.5 mg<br />Non-medicinal Ingredients: Glycerine (vegetarian), water.</p>\n<p>QUALITY, PURITY AND POTENCY GUARANTEED.</p>\n<p>Free from wheat, gluten, dairy, eggs, nuts, peanuts, fish, shellfish, sugar,<br />yeast, or artificial colours, flavours, and preservatives.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Grapefruit Seed Extract 90 tablets</span></p>\n<p>Medicinal Ingredients: Each vegetarian tablet contains:<br />Bioflavonoids from certified organic grapefruit (Citrus paradisi) seed extract &hellip;.......................&hellip;5 mg<br />Vitamin C from certified organic acerola (Malpighia emarginata) fruit &hellip;&hellip;..........................&hellip;.8.5 mg<br />Non-medicinal Ingredients: Organic maltodextrin, carnauba wax, silicon dioxide.<br /><br />QUALITY, PURITY AND POTENCY<br />GUARANTEED.</p>\n<p><br />Free from wheat, gluten, dairy, eggs,<br />nuts, peanuts, fish, shellfish, sugar,<br />yeast, artificial colours, flavours or<br />preservatives.</p>', '<p>Grapefruit Seed Extract 50mL</p>\n<p>Directions for Use: Adults: As respiratory and gastrointestinal aid: Take 8-10 drops (0.4-0.6 mL) 2-3 times daily, with food.<br />For diarrhoea relief: Take 10-15 drops (0.5-0.75 mL) in water or juice, four times daily.<br />For Candida support: Take 12-18 drops (0.6-0.9 mL) 2-3 times daily.<br />Contraindications: Do not take if you are pregnant, breastfeeding or have a bile duct obstruction.<br />Cautions: Consult a healthcare practitioner if symptoms persist or worsen. Do not use if the seal is broken. Keep out of reach of children. Store in a cool dry place to preserve<br />freshness.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Grapefruit Seed Extract 90 tablets</p>\n<p>Directions for Use: Adults: As respiratory and gastrointestinal aid: Take 1 tablet up to 3 times<br />daily, with food. For candida relief: Take 1-2 tablets 2-3 times daily. For enteric parasites: Take 4<br />tablets, 4 times daily, with food.<br />Contra-Indications: Do not take if you are pregnant, breastfeeding or have a bile duct obstruction.<br />Cautions: Consult a healthcare practitioner if symptoms persist or worsen.<br />Do not use if the seal is broken. Keep out of reach of children. Store in a cool dry<br />place to preserve freshness.</p>', 'Grapefruit Seed Extract| anti-microbial| benzethonium chloride free|benzalkonium', 'Grapefruit Seed Extract, free from benzethonium chloride and benzalkonium chloride, is a broad spectrum anti-microbial, available in  liquid drops and vegetarian tablets.   ', 'Extrait de pépins de pamplemousse Yeast Buster', '', '', '', '<p>Cette combinaison d\\''extrait de p&eacute;pins de pamplemousse aide &agrave; neutraliser les virus, la levure, les champignons, les parasites, les vers et les bact&eacute;ries. Facilement tol&eacute;r&eacute;, extr&ecirc;mement puissant et ne nuisant pas aux bonnes bact&eacute;ries. Utilis&eacute; pour la candidose, les parasites, l\\''acn&eacute;, les rhumes, les grippes, les feux sauvages, les blessures, les irritations cutan&eacute;es, les sinusites, les ulc&egrave;res et la diarrh&eacute;e. Fait &agrave; partir de pamplemousse et d\\''origan certifi&eacute;s biologiques, ce liquide est citricidal &agrave; 60%, dans une base de glyc&eacute;rine. Offert en deux formats, peut &eacute;galement &ecirc;tre utilis&eacute; dilu&eacute; comme nettoyeur de fruits et l&eacute;gumes ou simplement comme nettoyant.</p>', '', '', '', '', 1, 'No', '', 'Grapefruit Seed Extract Tabs NPN# 80044133; Grapefruit Seed Extract Liquid NPN#  80044131', 'Active');
