(12, 'ad-09-02', 3, 'DDS Original', '', 'Contributes to a natural healthy gut flora.', '<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Key Benefits:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Utilizes Lactobacillus acidophilus (DDS-1&reg; strain)</li>\n<li>Contains 5 billion colony forming units (CFU) per serving</li>\n<li>Promotes overall digestive health and regular bowel movements</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div id=\\"_com_1\\" class=\\"msocomtxt\\"><!--[if !supportAnnotations]--></div>\n<!--[endif]--></div>\n</div>', '<p><span class=\\"bold\\">DDS Probiotic Family Overview:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Superior robust strain: Survives stomach acid and bile for a healthy intestinal flora; human origin for easy adaptability.&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Clinically researched proprietary formulas: Clinically proven in double blind placebo human trials.&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Fortified with prebiotics:&nbsp; Feeds, nourishes and increases probiotic bacteria.</li>\n<li>Complete family care: Full line from infant to urgent care.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Restore the healthy balance of intestinal flora</span></p>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Repair the gut ecosystem disrupted by a disturbance (i.e. infection, antibiotic induced diarrhea, etc.)</span></p>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Reclaim a healthy gut.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">&nbsp;Sources:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\\"http://www.cabdirect.org/abstracts/19800465097.html;jsessionid=46EAA31964AC7726A6DB839218835E16\\" target=\\"_blank\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: &quot;HelveticaNeueLTStd-Lt&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: HelveticaNeueLTStd-Lt;\\">Ayebo, A. D., I. A. Angelo, and K. M. Shahani. 1980. Effect of ingesting </span><em><span style=\\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: &quot;HelveticaNeueLTStd-LtIt&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: HelveticaNeueLTStd-LtIt;\\">Lactobacillus acidophilus </span></em></a><span style=\\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Helvetic