es personnes vivant dans l&rsquo;h&eacute;misph&egrave;re nord n&rsquo;ont pas un  apport suffisant en vitamine D. Inno-Cal-Mag offre maintenant 1000 UI de vitamine D3 par portion afin d&rsquo;assurer la meilleure assimilation de min&eacute;raux qui soit et une absorption in&eacute;gal&eacute;e du calcium.</p>', '', '', '', '', '', 3, 'No', '', '80031383', 'Active'),
(22, 'vt0103', 1, 'Formula HH Plus', '30+ synergistic  ingredients PLUS Vitamin K2', 'Supports healthy heart function, promotes proper circulation and vascular flow. ', '<p>Building on the success of Formula HH and its 30+ synergistic ingredients, Formula HH PLus includes the patented Vitamin K2 (MK-7)for more complete bio-availability and bio-activity, thus ensuring maximum functionality.</p>\n<h6><span class=\\"bold\\">Key Benefits:</span></h6>\n<ul>\n<li>Promotes healthy cardiovascular circulation</li>\n<li>Helps inhibit arterial plaque formation and may reverse existing plaques &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Formulation acts synergistically for an arterial cleansing effect</li>\n<li>Includes&nbsp;patented Vitamin K2 (MK-7)&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>', '<p>The blood carries nutrients and oxygen to every cell in the body, and carries away wastematerials from those same cells for excretion. The unimpeded flow of bloodthroughout the whole body is critical for every body function and for keeping energy levels high.Atherosclerosis begins when something injures the inner lining of an artery.Many physicians now believe that the initial damage may be caused by free radical moleculescreated from exposure to environmental pollution, poor quality food, cigarette smoke and highlevels of stress. As with any injury, the body attempts to repair the wound in the artery lining. Inthe process, a destructive chain reaction can be set into motion, which results in thickening ofthe arterial wall; this thickening, in turn, obstructs the artery. Arterial obstructions are calledplaques or atheromas. As the plaque grows inside an artery, blood flow is reduced, withpotentially very serious health consequences. Clearing arterial plaques can improve circulationand quality of life while reducing the risk of serious and debilitating cardiovascular illnesses.</p>\n<h5><span class=\\"bold\\">Formula HH Plus has 30+ Synergistic ingredients including Vitamin K2:</span></h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Vitamin K associated with a reduced risk of coronary heart disease. Includes the patented Vitamin K2 (MK-7)for more complete  bio-availability and bio-activity, thus ensuring maximum  functionality.&nbsp;Due to its long half-life in the blood stream, vitamin K2  (MK-7) enables effective carboxylation of K-dependent proteins, such as  osteocalcin and MGP. Once activated, these proteins are a crucial  milestone for arterial health and ensure calcium is absorbed from the  blood into the bone mass, giving better calcium utilization without  adding arterial calcification risks.</li>\n<li>Niacin is proven for cholesterol lowering effects and its ability to raise the levels of HDL (the &ldquo;good&rdquo; cholesterol)</li>\n<li>Pomegranate extract, an ingredient with antioxidant, anti-inflammatory, and anti-plaque benefits</li>\n<li>High Potency Antioxidant Vitamins C, E, A, and B</li>\n<li>Folic Acid for homocysteine reduction</li>\n<li>Vitamin D required for optimal cardiovascular health</li>\n<li>Magnesium normalizes blood pressure and prevents arrhythmias</li>\n<li>Potassium supports healthy muscle contraction, transmitting electrochemical impulses and maintaining blood pressure</li>\n<li>Chromium helps maintain stable blood sugar levels</li>\n<li>Selenium protects lipids from oxidation</li>\n<li>Betaine hydrochloride helps with nutrient break-down and absorption</li>\n<li>Choline emulsifies and reduces stickiness fat</li>\n<li>Cysteine is a chelating agent and free radical scavenger</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>For over 30 years, Innovite Health has been inspiring wellness. When the body&rsquo;s core systems work in synergy, optimal health can be achieved. Our goal to nourish and heal the body from the inside out: restoring nutrients and repairing damage so you can reclaim your health. Our nutritional foundation is built from the latest research and clinical evidence. Safe, natural and effective &ndash; Innovite Health for your body&rsquo;s needs, at every stage of life.</p>', '<div><span lang=\\"JA\\"><span lang=\\"JA\\">\n<div>Medicinal Ingredients:</div>\n</span></span>\n<div>Each vegetarian tablet contains:</div>\n<div>Vitamin A</div>\n<div>(palmitate).........1200 mcg RAE (4000 IU)</div>\n<div>Vitamin D3</div>\n<div>(cholecalciferol)............1.625 mcg (65 IU)</div>\n<div>Vitamin E (d-alpha tocopheryl</div>\n<div>acetate)......................43.5 mg AT (65 IU)</div>\n<div>Vitamin C (ascorbic acid).................. 300 mg</div>\n<div>Vitamin C (calcium ascorbate) ..........100 mg</div>\n<div>Vitamin B1 (thiamine hydrochloride)... 20 mg</div>\n<div>Vitamin B2 (riboflavin) .......................... 5 mg</div>\n<div>Vitamin B6</div>\n<div>(pyridoxine hydrochloride)..............15 mg</div>\n<div>Vitamin B12</div>\n<div>(cyanocobalamin)......................... 25 mcg</div>\n<div>Niacin</div>\n<div>(inositol hexanicotinate)................100 mg</div>\n<div>Pantothenic Acid</div>\n<div>(calcium d-pantothenate)................50 mg</div>\n<div>Folic Acid .........................................0.04 mg</div>\n<div>Biotin..................................................10 mcg</div>\n<div>Vitamin K2 (MK-7) .............................. 5 mcg</div>\n<div>Magnesium (oxide)..............................40 mg</div>\n<div>Potassium (chloride, citrate)................40 mg</div>\n<div>Calcium (carbonate) ...........................30 mg</div>\n<div>Manganese (gluconate)......................0.5 mg</div>\n<div>Zinc (gluconate).................................... 3 mg</div>\n<div>Chromium (HVP chelate)...................20 mcg</div>\n<div>Selenium (HVP chelate) ...................25 mcg</div>\n<div>Iodine (potassium iodide) ..............0.025 mg</div>\n<div>Choline Bitartrate.................................70 mg</div>\n<div>Inositol ..................................................5 mg</div>\n<div>DL-Methionine ....................................25 mg</div>\n<div>Betaine Hydrochloride ........................24 mg</div>\n<div>L-Cysteine Hydrochloride .................100 mg</div>\n</div>\n<div>Pomegranate (Punica granatum) Extract</div>\n<div>\n<div>(70% ellagic acid)...........................15 mg</div>\n<span lang=\\"JA\\"><span lang=\\"JA\\">\n<div>Non-medicinal Ingredients:</div>\n</span></span></div>\n<div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n<div>Microcrystalline cellulose, colloidal silicon</div>\n<div>dioxide, magnesium stearate, hydroxypropyl</div>\n</div>\n<div>methylcellulose, natural vanilla flavour.</div>\n<div><span lang=\\"JA\\"><span lang=\\"JA\\">Free from </span></span>sugar, dairy, wheat, gluten,</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>corn, eggs, soy, yeast, fish, shellfish, nuts,</div>\n<div>peanuts, artificial colours, flavours and</div>\n<div>preservatives.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n</div>', '<div><span lang=\\"JA\\"><span lang=\\"JA\\">&nbsp;</span></span></div>\n<div><span class=\\"bold\\" lang=\\"JA\\"><span lang=\\"JA\\">Directions for Use: </span></span>(Adults): Take 2 vegetarian tablets daily.</div>\n<div><span lang=\\"JA\\"><span lang=\\"JA\\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\\"JA\\"><span lang=\\"JA\\">&nbsp;</span></span></div>\n<div><span class=\\"bold\\" lang=\\"JA\\"><span lang=\\"JA\\">Cautions: </span></span>For adult use only. Consult a healthcare practitioner prior to use if you</div>\n<div>\n<div>are pregnant or breastfeeding, or if you are taking blood thinners.</div>\n<div>Do not use if the seal is broken. Keep out</div>\n<div>of reach of children. Store in a cool, dry</div>\n<div>place to preserve freshness.</div>\n<span lang=\\"JA\\"><span lang=\\"JA\\">\n<div><span class=\\"bold\\">QUALITY, PURITY AND POTENCY&nbsp;GUARANTEED.</span></div>\n</span></span><span lang=\\"JA\\"><span lang=\\"JA\\">&nbsp;</span></span></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n</div>', 'Formula HH Plus  | 30+ syngergistic ingredients PLUS Vitamin K2 for heart health ', 'Formula HH PLus includes the patented Vitamin K2 (MK-7)for more complete bio-availability and bio-activity, thus ensuring maximum functionality.  ', 'Formula HH Plus', '', '', '', '<p>La maladie cardiovasculaire est la cause de d&eacute;c&egrave;s la plus r&eacute;pandue parmi les Canadiens. Malheureusement, il est facile de d&eacute;velopper une maladie cardiovasculaire et, en termes simples, il a &eacute;t&eacute; prouv&eacute; r&eacute;cemment que la calcification art&eacute;rielle est le plus grand signe avant-coureur de crise cardiaque et d\\''accident c&eacute;r&eacute;brovasculaire fatal, encore plus que des taux malsains de cholest&eacute;rol*. De nombreux m&eacute;decins croient &agrave; pr&eacute;sent qu\\''une exposition &agrave; la pollution environnementale et &agrave; la fum&eacute;e de cigarette, la consommation d\\''aliments de mauvaise qualit&eacute;, et des niveaux &eacute;lev&eacute;s de stress contribuent aux dommages art&eacute;riels et &agrave; l\\''accumulation de plaque, et &eacute;ventuellement &agrave; la maladie cardiovasculaire. Les nutriments appropri&eacute;s, utilis&eacute;s dans la bonne combinaison, peuvent aider &agrave; conserver le c&oelig;ur et les art&egrave;res en sant&eacute; et forts tout au cours de la vie.  Des &eacute;tudes r&eacute;centes r&eacute;v&egrave;lent qu\\''un apport suffisant en vitamine K est reli&eacute; &agrave; une incidence r&eacute;duite de maladies coronariennes**.  Formule HH avec vitamine K est un suppl&eacute;ment puissant de multivitamines et min&eacute;raux, et seulement deux comprim&eacute;s par jour apporteront un soutien continu pour le maintien de la sant&eacute; de votre c&oelig;ur et aideront &agrave; r&eacute;duire le risque de d&eacute;velopper une maladie cardiovasculaire***.  Formule HH Plus contient &eacute;galement de la niacine dont l\\''efficacit&eacute; a &eacute;t&eacute; prouv&eacute;e &agrave; abaisser le cholest&eacute;rol en plus d\\''&eacute;lever les taux de \\"bon\\" cholest&eacute;rol.   L\\''extrait de grenade est un autre ingr&eacute;dient dans la Formule HH Plus, qui a &eacute;t&eacute; ajout&eacute; pour ses bienfaits antioxydants, anti-inflammatoires et antiplaquettaires. Deux comprim&eacute;s sont &eacute;quivalents &agrave; un verre de jus de grenade frais.  *Vascular Health and Risk Management, Avril 2008. **Journal of Nutrition, Novembre 2004. ***Le fabricant ne garantit aucun r&eacute;sultat car les r&eacute;sultats varient selon la personne.</p>', '', '', '', '', 5, 'No', '', '80031981', 'Active');
