(23, 'ad2718', 2, 'Yeast Buster™  Black Walnut Complex', '', 'Promotes gastrointestinal health', '<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\"><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt; line-height: 115%;\\">Black Walnut Complex is a balanced formula to help prevent parasitic infections and speed recovery from an active infection. This formula not only kills parasites, but also helps remove toxins out of the body as parasites die-off and release toxins.</span></p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\"><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt; line-height: 115%;\\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\\"font-size: 8.0pt; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\\"><span class=\\"bold\\">Key Benefits:</span></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">All ingredients in the formulation are wild crafted and/or organically grown</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Synergistic ingredients provide the following therapeutic benefits:</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Helps expel intestinal worms and parasites (green hulls)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Anti-Microbial benefits (Cloves bud)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Expels parasitic worms (Wormwood aerial herb)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Eliminates thread worms, nematodes, and ascaris (Quassia wood)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Modulates the immune system and to help the body increase its own defences to assist in the elimination of parasites and other microbial infections.(Reishi mushroom)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Provides anti-inflammatory, anti-malarial, antibacterial, antifungal, and anti-parasitic benefits (Pau D&rsquo;arco bark)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Promote elimination of toxins produced by parasites and other microbes (Boneset whole herb)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Anti-spasmodic, anti-inflammatory agent that helps heal wounds including internal gastrointestinal ulcers or wounds from infection (Calendula flower)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Combats nausea which may be caused by toxins released by parasites (Ginger root)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Available in tincture and capsules to enhance compliance and rapid microbial elimination</span></li>\n</ul>', '<p>Innovite Health&rsquo;s Black Walnut Complex is a balanced formula to help prevent</p>\n<p>parasitic infections and speed recovery from an active infection. It\\''s produced in</p>\n<p>adherence to growing, harvesting, production and manufacturing principles of</p>\n<p>traditional medicine, and whenever possible organically-grown or wild-crafted herbs</p>\n<p>are used. Innovite Health\\''s Black Walnut complex contains:</p>\n<p>&bull; Black Walnut (Juglans nigra) green hulls: Using green hulls is essential for efficacy;</p>\n<p>therefore, choosing the precise moments for harvesting is very important, and only</p>\n<p>comes with decades of experience.</p>\n<p>&bull; Cloves (Syzygium aromaticum) bud: Traditionally used as an anti-microbial; also</p>\n<p>used as an anti-spasmotic to help with digestion and cramping.</p>\n<p>&bull; Wormwood (Artemisia absinthium) aerial herb: Well-known herb traditionally used</p>\n<p>as an anthelmintic, but also helps with digestive complaints.</p>\n<p>&bull; Quassia wood (Picraena excelsa): An exotic rainforest wood useful against thread</p>\n<p>worms, nematodes, a