(25, 'vt0120', 1, 'INNO-KRILL', '100% Pure Neptune Krill Oil (NKO®) ', 'Cardiovascular and cognitive support', '<p>This 100% pure krill oil carries omega-3s in phospholipids &ndash;&nbsp;the building blocks that help regulate cellular transport and aid cell membrane protection by facilitating fatty acid delivery to the cells. &nbsp;Capsule format helps reduce reflux.</p>\n<h5><span class=\\"bold\\">Key Benefits:</span></h5>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\\"bold\\">Improved Absorption:</span> A high concentration of phospholipids attached to the omega-3 fatty acids increase the bioavailability and absorption of nutrients and provide all the benefits associated to omega-3 fatty acids.</li>\n<li><span class=\\"bold\\">Powerful Antioxidant Protection</span>: Unique antioxidants&mdash;including astaxanthin and a novel marine flavonoid&mdash;may protect you from the adverse effects and damage caused by free radicals. There is 47 times more anti-oxidant protection in Inno-Krill than in most fish oils.</li>\n<li><span class=\\"bold\\">Clinically Proven</span>: Clinically demonstrated ability to:    \n<ul>\n<li>Protect the heart,</li>\n<li>Act as an anti-inflammatory</li>\n<li>Alleviate premenstrual symptoms,</li>\n<li>Improve skin health</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;', '<p>Derived from Antarctic krill (a shrimp-like creature inhabiting the cold waters of the Antarctic Ocean), Inno Krill is rich in omega-3 fatty acids which are among the most researched of all nutrients and are acclaimed for their heart-healthy properties.&nbsp;Inno Krill is different from other marine oils due to the high concentration of phospholipids attached to the omega 3 fatty acids which act as superior delivery systems of nutrients.&nbsp;In&nbsp;addition, it contains a powerful antioxidant known as astaxanthin, which&nbsp;imbues the oil with exceptional protection against oxidation and rancidity&mdash;a&nbsp;property that does not exist in any fish oil.&nbsp;One of krill oil&rsquo;s most promising actions is its ability to improve inflammation&nbsp;and blood lipid levels. Recent research suggests that krill oil may be even&nbsp;more effective at improving cholesterol levels than fish oil. &nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h5><span><strong>Sources:</strong>&nbsp; </span></h5>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\\"http://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/jf900903e\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Grandois LG, Marchioni E, Zhao M, Giuffrida F, Ennahar S, Bindler F (June 2009). &ldquo;Investigation of natural phosphatidylcholine sources: separation and identification by liquid chromatography - electronspray ionization - tandem mass spectrometry (LC-ESI-MS2) of molecular species&rdquo;. Journal of Agricultural and Food Chemistry 57 (14): 6014&ndash;6020. doi:10.1021/jf900903e. PMID 19545117</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\\"http://www.pubmedcentral.nih.gov/articlerender.fcgi?tool=pmcentrez&amp;artid=3024512.\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Winther B, Hoem N, Berge K, Reubsaet L (September 2010). &ldquo;Elucidation of phosphatidylcholine composition in krill oil extracted from Euphausia Superba&rdquo;. Lipids 46 (1): 25&ndash;36. doi:10.1007/s11745-010-3472-6. PMC 3024512. PMID 20848234.&nbsp;</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>For over 30 years, Innovite Health has been inspiring wellness. When the body&rsquo;s core systems work in synergy, optimal health can be achieved. Our goal to nourish and heal the body from the inside out: restoring nutrients and repairing damage so you can reclaim your health. Our nutritional foundation is built from the latest research and clinical evidence. Safe, natural and effective &ndash; Innovite Health for your body&rsquo;s needs, at every stage of life.</p>', '<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Medicinal ingredients:</span><br /> Each softgel contains:<br /> 1000 mg of 100% pure NKO providing:<br /> Vitamin A - 100 IU<br /> Vitamin E - 0.50 IU<br /> Omega-3 fatty acids - 300 mg<br /> EPA - 150 mg<br /> DHA - 90 mg<br /> Omega-6 fatty acids - 20 mg<br /> Omega-9 fatty acids - 100 mg<br /> Phospholipids - 400 mg<br /> Astaxanthin - 1.26 mg<br /> Choline - 74 mg<br /><br /> <span class=\\"bold\\">Non-Medicinal Ingredients:</span> Fish gelatin from tilapia scales, glycerine, purified water</p>', '<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Directions for Use:</span><br /> Adults (19 years and over): Take 1 softgel once or twice daily with a meal, or as directed by a healthcare practitioner.</p>', '', '', 'INNO-KRILL', '', '', '', '<p>D&eacute;riv&eacute;e du krill de l\\''Antarctique (cr&eacute;ature de petite taille ressemblant &agrave; une crevette et habitant les eaux froides de l\\''Oc&eacute;an Antarctique), l\\''huile de krill Neptune (NKO&reg;) a prouv&eacute; son habilet&eacute; en clinique &agrave; prot&eacute;ger le c&oelig;ur, &agrave; agir comme anti-inflammatoire, &agrave; soulager les sympt&ocirc;mes du syndrome pr&eacute;menstruel, &agrave; rehausser la sant&eacute; de la peau et &agrave; soutenir le bien-&ecirc;tre.   L\\''huile NKO&reg; est riche en acides gras om&eacute;ga-3 qui figurent parmi les nutriments les plus recherch&eacute;s et qui sont reconnus pour leurs vertus favorisant la sant&eacute; du c&oelig;ur. L\\''huile NKO&reg; est diff&eacute;rente des autres huiles marines en ce sens que ses acides gras om&eacute;ga-3 se lient &agrave; des phospholipides qui agissent comme un syst&egrave;me de livraison sup&eacute;rieur, ce qui r&eacute;sulte en une meilleure absorption (biodisponibilit&eacute;) et une plus grande bioactivit&eacute; &agrave; des doses plus faibles comparativement aux autres huiles de poisson.   Pourquoi Inno-Krill?  Absorption am&eacute;lior&eacute;e Seulement une ou deux petites capsules par jour suffisent pour b&eacute;n&eacute;ficier des vertus &eacute;tonnantes du Inno-Krill NKO&reg;. Le m&eacute;canisme de liaison des phospholipides augmente la biodisponibilit&eacute; des om&eacute;ga-3, augmente le ratio d&rsquo;om&eacute;ga-3 &agrave; om&eacute;ga-6, et soutient le fonctionnement des membranes cellulaires saines.   Protection antioxydante puissante Les antioxydants particuliers, entre autres l\\''astaxanthine et un flavono&iuml;de marin unique en son genre, pourraient vous prot&eacute;ger des effets ind&eacute;sirables et des dommages caus&eacute;s par les radicaux libres. La capacit&eacute; antioxydante de Inno-Krill NKO&reg; est 47 fois plus &eacute;lev&eacute;e que celle de la plupart des huiles de poisson sur le march&eacute;.   Aucun contaminant  Comme le krill se situe au bas de l\\''&eacute;chelle alimentaire et provient des eaux profondes de l\\''Oc&eacute;an Antarctique, vous n\\''avez pas &agrave; vous inqui&eacute;ter de l\\''accumulation nocive de mercure, de m&eacute;taux lourds et autres toxines.   Ressources durables  Le krill est une source hautement renouvelable. Ce crustac&eacute; fait partie de la plus grande biomasse de l\\''oc&eacute;an et le risque de causer sa disparition &agrave; cause d\\''une surexploitation est minime.   Stabilit&eacute;  Inno-Krill NKO&reg; est plus stable que la plupart des huiles de poisson en raison de sa teneur &eacute;lev&eacute;e en antioxydants, ce qui signifie que cette huile ne s\\''oxydera pas dans l\\''organisme et ne rancira pas.   Sans &eacute;ructation avec arri&egrave;re-go&ucirc;t de poisson  Aucun cas d\\''&eacute;ructation ou autres effets ind&eacute;sirables n\\''ont &eacute;t&eacute; rapport&eacute;s &agrave; des doses &eacute;lev&eacute;es.   Valid&eacute;e en clinique L\\''huile NKO&reg; est le seul produit d\\''huile de krill de l\\''Antarctique &agrave; avoir d&eacute;montr&eacute; en clinique ses bienfaits &agrave; la sant&eacute; relativement aux apports nutritionnels de r&eacute;f&eacute;rence (ANREF) pour le march&eacute;. Ces r&eacute;sultats sont publi&eacute;s dans les revues &agrave; comit&eacute; de lecture.  Autres raisons: &bull;Innocuit&eacute; et stabilit&eacute; &eacute;prouv&eacute;es. &bull;Aucun gras trans. &bull;Fabriqu&eacute;es selon les normes des BPF. &bull;Approbation r&eacute;glementaire multinationale. &bull;Brevets internationaux.  Inno-Krill NKO&reg; vous livre 500 mg d\\''huile de krill de Neptune pure &agrave; 100% par g&eacute;lule. Cette forme posologique et la quantit&eacute; sont exactement les m&ecirc;mes que celles utilis&eacute;es dans de nombreux essais en clinique sur des humains.</p>', '', '', '', '', 6, 'No', '', 'Inno-Krill (500 mg) 80030058; Inno-Krill (1000 mg) 80034422', 'Active'),
(26, 'sp0118', 5, 'Lutein ', '', '', '<p>Lutein will allow you to restore the healthy levels of lutein in your eyes. This will allow you to rebuild your healthy vision and eye health in order to reclaim the gift of a healthy vision.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Key Benefits:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Formulated with&nbsp;&nbsp;FloraGLO&reg; Lutein, the most researched lutein in the market with multiple trials supporting its efficacy and quality. &nbsp;It is the most bioavailable and most absorbable form of Lutein.</li>\n<li>Promotes the health of the macula, retina and lens in the eye</li>\n<li>Reduces the risk of age related macular degeneration (AMD) and cataracts</li>\n<li>Improves night vision and glare tolerance</li>\n<li>Sourced from marigold flowers and purified from marigold flower oleoresin</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\">&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Nearly half of all North Americans aren&rsquo;t getting enough lutein each day&mdash; an essential nutrient critical to maintaining healthy vision. Antioxidants keep your eyes healthy, improve visual performance and help reduce the risk of certain eye conditions as you age. Although you are born with protective lutein pigment in your eye, these levels generally decrease with age. Since your body can&rsquo;t produce lutein, it&rsquo;s important to replenish your lutein levels through diet and nutritional supplementation</p>', '<p>Each softgel contains:<br /> FloraGLO Marigold (Tagetes erecta) flower extract	 500 mg<br /> Providing:<br /> Lutein	25 mg<br /> Zeaxanthin	1.1 mg<br /><br /> Non-Medicinal Ingredients: Gelatin, Glycerin, Safflower Oil, Sunflower lecithin, Purified Water, Annatto Seed Extract</p>', '<p>Directions for Use:<br /> Adult Dosage: Take one softgel daily with food, or as directed by a qualified healthcare practitioner.</p>', '', '', 'Lutéine ', '', '', '', '<p>La lut&eacute;ine est un antioxydant naturel propre &agrave; la sant&eacute; des yeux. Le produit Lut&eacute;ine d\\''Inno-Vite favorise la sant&eacute; de la macula, de la r&eacute;tine et du cristallin de l\\''&oelig;il, r&eacute;duisant le risque de d&eacute;g&eacute;n&eacute;rescence maculaire li&eacute;e &agrave; l\\''&acirc;ge (DMLA) et de cataractes. La lut&eacute;ine s\\''est &eacute;galement av&eacute;r&eacute;e efficace pour am&eacute;liorer la vision nocturne et la tol&eacute;rance &agrave; l\\''&eacute;blouissement.</p>', '', '', '', '', 4, 'No', '', '80020098', 'Active'),
(27, 'sp0111', 5, 'INNO-VISION', '', 'Helps to maintain healthy eyesight and skin membranes; also promotes night vision by improving glare tolerance.', '<h5><span class=\\"bold\\">Key Benefits:</span></h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Contains all the essential ingredients to provide complete vision support</li>\n<li>Helps maintain healthy eyesight and skin membranes</li>\n<li>Promotes night vision by improving glare tolerance</li>\n</ul>', '<p>Results from the Age-Related Eye Disease Study (AREDS) sponsored by the National Eye Institute showed that a combination of high levels of antioxidant vitamins A, C and E, in combination with the minerals zinc and copper significantly reduces the risk of advanced macular degeneration and its associated vision loss.</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Medicinal Ingredients: Each capsule contains:</p>\n<p>Vitamin A (palmitate).....................250 mcg RAE (833.33 IU)</p>\n<p>Beta carotene..............................625 mcg RAE (4166.67 IU)</p>\n<p>Vitamin C (ascorbic acid, calcium ascorbate)......&hellip;83.33 mg</p>\n<p>Vitamin D3 (cholcalciferol)....................8.33 mcg (333.33 IU)</p>\n<p>Vitamin E</p>\n<p>(d-alpha tocopheryl succinate)....44.67 mg AT (66.67 IU)</p>\n<p>Vitamin K2 (MK-7)&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.....................................3.33 mcg</p>\n<p>B1 (Thiamine hydrochloride).....................................6.67 mg</p>\n<p>B2 (Riboflavin)...........................................................6.67 mg</p>\n<p>B3 (Niacin)................................................................3.33 mg</p>\n<p>B3 (Niacinamide).......................................................6.67 mg</p>\n<p>B5 (calcium d-pantothenate).....................................6.67 mg</p>\n<p>B6 (pyridoxine hydrochloride) ..................................6.67 mg</p>\n<p>Folate (folic acid) ................................................133.33 mcg</p>\n<p>B12 (cyanocobalamin).........................................133.33 mcg</p>\n<p>Calcium (ca