(29, 'vl10183', 5, 'Iron ', 'Natural fruit punch flavoured liquid iron', 'Helps prevent iron deficiency', '<p>Iron is essential for keeping the body functioning at its best. Most of the iron in the body is needed to form hemoglobin, a component of red blood cells. Hemoglobin&rsquo;s role is to transport oxygen in the body to ensure that some of the most important body functions are supported with the energy that they require to properly keep you healthy. (i.e. breathing, moving, etc.</p>\n<h5><span class=\\"bold\\">Key Benefits:</span></h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Formulated with ferrous gluconate, an organically-bound form of iron proven to be the most highly absorbable form of this essential mineral</li>\n<li>Formulated using AbsorbMax&trade; technology for better taste and results</li>\n<li>Great natural fruit punch taste in easy-to-take liquid form &nbsp;</li>\n<li>Contains 93% of the recommended daily allowance of iron for women</li>\n</ul>', '<p>Iron deficiency is very common, especially among women in child-bearing age. This can cause a general lack of energy, a short attention span, fatigue, poor appetite, weight loss, pale appearance and irritability.</p>', '<p><span style=\\"font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: small;\\"> </span></p>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Medicinal Ingredients:</span> Each tbs (15 mL) contains:</p>\n<p>Iron (gluconate) &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;16.7 mg</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Non-medicinal Ingredients:</span> Purified water, concentrated apple</p>\n<p>juice, concentrated grape juice, honey, natural anise flavour,</p>\n<p>potassium sorbate.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">QUALITY, PURITY AND POTENCY GUARANTEED.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Free from GMO,wheat, starch, gluten, dairy, corn,</p>\n<p>eggs, soy, yeast,nuts, fish, shellfish,artificial colours and flavours</p>', '<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Directions: </span>Adults and Children: Take 1 tbs (15 mL) once or</p>\n<p>twice daily with meals, or as directed by a healthcare practitioner.</p>\n<p>Take a few hours before or after taking other medications.</p>\n<p>Shake well before each use. Refrigerate after opening.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Cautions / Warnings:</span> Keep out of reach of children.</p>\n<p>There is enough drug in this package to seriously</p>\n<p>harm a child. Some people may experience</p>\n<p>constipation, diarrhoea, and/or vomiting</p>', '', '', 'Fer liquide ', '', '', '', '<p>Le fer est essentiel pour que le corps fonctionne &agrave; son meilleur. La plus grande partie du fer dans notre corps sert &agrave; la formation de l\\''h&eacute;moglobine, un constituant des globules rouges. Le r&ocirc;le de l\\''h&eacute;moglobine est de transporter l\\''oxyg&egrave;ne dans les cellules du corps afin d\\''assurer que vous obteniez le maximum d\\''&eacute;nergie des aliments que vous consommez, pour respirer, pour cro&icirc;tre, pour vous d&eacute;placer et pour faire battre votre c&oelig;ur.<br /> Une carence en fer est tr&egrave;s courante, surtout chez les femmes en &acirc;ge de procr&eacute;er, et peut entra&icirc;ner un manque d\\''&eacute;nergie en g&eacute;n&eacute;ral, une mauvaise concentration, la fatigue, un app&eacute;tit m&eacute;diocre, une perte de poids, un teint p&acirc;le et l\\''irritabilit&eacute;.<strong><br /> Pourquoi choisir le Fer liquide d\\''Inno-Vite? <br /> </strong> Le Fer liquide d\\''Inno-Vite offre la forme la plus assimilable de fer pour demeurer en sant&eacute; et optimiste &agrave; tous les &acirc;ges. Chaque cuiller&eacute;e &agrave; table du produit Fer liquide d\\''Inno-Vite procure 16,7 mg de fer sous forme de gluconate &agrave; liaison organique, hautement assimilable. Cet apport comble 93% de l\\''apport quotidien recommand&eacute; chez les femmes.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>&Agrave; liaison organique.</li>\n<li>Sans levure et sans gluten.</li>\n<li>Go&ucirc;t naturel agr&eacute;able.</li>\n<li>Sans OGM (organismes g&eacute;n&eacute;tiquement modifi&eacute;s).</li>\n</ul>', '', '', '', '', 2, 'No', '', 'NPN 80015987', 'Active'),
(30, 'ad2719', 2, 'UTI Protect', '', 'Helps prevent prevent recurrent bladder and urinary tract infections (UTIs)', '<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 8.0pt; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\\"><span class=\\"bold\\">Key Benefits</span></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Treats and prevents recurring cystitis and UTIs by inhibiting E. coli&rsquo;s ability to attach to the walls of the bladder and urinary tract</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Acts as a diuretic to flush out the bladder and urinary tract</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Reduces dependence to antibiotics</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Synergistic formulation provides the following therapeutic benefits:</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Prevents adhesion of E. Colito the urinary tract wall (Cranberry extract)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">&ldquo;Coats&rdquo; the E. Coli so that it cannot bind to the bladder and urinary tract cells to cause infections (D-Mannose)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Turns the urinary tract and bladder walls into anti-adhesive surfaces facilitating the flushing of E.coli bacteria through regular urination (Grape Seed Extract)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Increases urination frequency to decrease the risk of UTIs by eliminating harmful bacteria via the urine (Parsley)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Inhibits the growth of E.Coli in the urinary tract (Garlic)</span></li>\n</ul>', '<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 8.0pt; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\\">While Escherichia coli (or E. coli) is normal bacteria found in every intestinal tract, it can have a disruptive effect on health when found in the urinary tract. In fact, 80-90% of all bladder infections (cystitis) and urinary tract infections (UTIs) can be attributed to E. coli being present in the urinary tract. This condition is 50 times more common in women and girls than in men.&nbsp;E. coli bacteria can also be present in the vagina, and migrate into the urethra and onward to the bladder, which is why many women end up with bladder infections.</span></p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 8.0pt; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\\"><br /> <strong>Symptoms of Bladder/Urinary Tract Infections </strong><br /> <br /> A variety of symptoms may indicate the presence of a bladder/urinary tract infections, and the intensity of those symptoms may range from mild to severe. Common symptoms may include:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Burning sensation upon urination</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Sensation of urgency to urinate without the ability to void completely</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Pink to reddish or cloudy urine</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Foul smelling urine</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\\">Lower abdominal pain</span></li>\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt; line-height: 115%;\\">Frequent urination</span></li>\n</ul>', '<p><span style=\\"font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: small;\\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Verdana;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: Calibri;\\">Medicinal Ingredients: Each vegetarian capsule contains:</span></span></p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Verdana;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: Calibri;\\">Cranberry (Vaccinium macrocarpon) fruit extract (90% fruit solids)&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;250 mg</span></span></p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Verdana;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: Calibri;\\">D-mannose&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;150 mg</span></span></p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Verdana;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: Calibri;\\">Parsley (Petroselinum crispum) leaf extract (4:1)&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.65 mg</span></span></p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Verdana;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: Calibri;\\">Garlic (Allium sativum) bulb extract (100:1)&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;..20 mg</span></span></p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Verdana;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: Calibri;\\">Grape (Vitis vinifera) seed extract (95% OPC)&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&he