(39, 'vt10230', 1, 'Bio-Active Folate', 'From Metafolin®', 'Helps the body to metabolize amino acids and form red blood cells  ', '<p>Metafolin<sup>&reg;</sup>&nbsp;is a&nbsp;bioactive form of folate and is primary used in the body to make DNA and RNA, the building blocks of cells, and this also helps prevent mutations to DNA that may lead to various illnesses. Both adults and children need folate to make normal red blood cells and prevent anemia.</p>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Key Benefits:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Essential for the production and maintenance of new cells</li>\n<li>Recommended for individuals that require folate repletion but might not be able to convert folate into the active form needed by the body</li>\n<li>Helps to reduce the risk of neural tube defects in newborns when taken during pregnancy</li>\n<li>Helps the body metabolize proteins.</li>\n</ul>', '<p>Metafolin<sup>&reg;</sup>&nbsp;((6S)-5-methyltetrahydrofolic acid, calcium salt or L-methylfolate) is the pure stable crystalline form of the naturally-occurring predominant form of folate. Folates are water-soluble B-vitamins, which play a key role in central metabolic pathways. Folates are, for example, needed for cell division or cell repair. Metafolin<sup>&reg;</sup>&nbsp;is L-methylfolate, the body\\''s preferred form of folate. Metafolin<sup>&reg;</sup>&nbsp;is directly usable by humans, directly involved in lowering homocysteine blood levels, and the only form of folate able to cross the blood-brain barrier.</p>\n<ul>\n</ul>', '<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><span class=\\"bold\\">Medicinal Ingredients:</span> Each tablet contains:</div>\n<div>Folate (as L-methylfolate, Metafolin&reg;) &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;...1000 mcg</div>\n<div>&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<div><span class=\\"bold\\">Non-medicinal Ingredients:</span> Cellulose, dicalcium phosphate, croscarmellose sodium,</div>\n<div>\n<div>vegetable stearate, silica.</div>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<div>Free from wheat, gluten, dairy,</div>\n<div>\n<div>corn, eggs, soy, nuts, peanuts, fish,</div>\n<div>shellfish, yeast, sugar, GMO,</div>\n<div>artificial colours, flavours and</div>\n<div>preservatives.</div>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Metafolin&reg; is a registered&nbsp;trademark of Merck KGaA,</div>\n<div>\n<div>Darmstadt, Germany.</div>\n</div>', '<div><span class=\\"bold\\">Directions for Use:</span> Adults (19 years and over): Take 1 tablet daily or as directed by a</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>healthcare practitioner.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><span class=\\"bold\\">Warnings</span>: Consult a healthcare practitioner prior to use if you are pregnant,</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>breastfeeding or on blood pressure medications or blood thinners.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><span class=\\"bold\\">Cautions:</span> Do not use if the seal is broken. Keep out of reach of children. Store in a cool</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>dry place to preserve freshness.</div>\n<div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n</div>', '', '', 'Folate Bio-actif', '', '', '', '<p>La forme bioactive de l\\''acide folique</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Le folate est essentiel &agrave; la production et au maintien des nouvelles cellules. Son r&ocirc;le primaire est de produire l\\''ADN et l\\''ARN, &eacute;l&eacute;ments de base des cellules, et il contribue &eacute;galement &agrave; pr&eacute;venir les mutations de l\\''ADN qui peuvent mener &agrave; diverses maladies. Les adultes ainsi que les enfants ont besoin de folate pour la bonne formation des globules rouges et pour la pr&eacute;vention de l\\''an&eacute;mie.<br /> 60 vegetarian tablets/comprim&eacute;s v&eacute;g&eacute;tariens INNO-VITE M&Eacute;THYLFOLATE aide &agrave; r&eacute;duire le risque de malformation du tube neural lorsque pris chaque jour avant ou au d&eacute;but de la grossesse. Il aide aussi le corps &agrave; m&eacute;taboliser les prot&eacute;ines.</p>', '', '', '', '', 8, 'No', '', '80042514', 'Active'),
(40, 'sb10225', 4, 'Inno-Cal-Mag Complex with extra Vitamin K2', '', 'Promotes healthy bones and the prevention of osteoporsis', '<p>INNO-CAL-MAG with Vitamin K2 is a comprehensive dietary supplement providing calcium and magnesium in a non-dairy, liquid formula for the maintenance of bones, cartilage, teeth and gums. This formula also offers Vitamin K2 in the form of MK-7 which is crucial for maximum calcium utilization.</p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\"><span class=\\"bold\\">Key Benefits:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Most comprehensive formulation of the Innovite Health&rsquo;s Calcium Magnesium formulations</li>\n<li>Strongly recommended for the treatment and prevention of osteoporosis</li>\n<li>This formula also offers Vitamin K2 in the form of MK-7 which is crucial for construction of healthy bones, as well as in the prevention of arterial calcium accumulation and the body&rsquo;s maximum calcium utilization</li>\n<li>Magnesium activates the enzyme that triggers formation of calcium crystals in bone, and converts vitamin D to its active form</li>\n<li>Synergistic formulation also contains Boron, Phosphorus, zinc, vitamin C, and Vitamin D3 to further support Calcium absorption</li>\n<li>Formulated with Calcium Phosphate, a highly bioavailable form of calcium</li>\n<li>Liquid Softgel allows for an easier digestion and absorption than tablets&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\">&nbsp;</p>', '<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\">INNO-CAL-MAG&reg; Family Overview</p>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\">Calcium has been the most obvious choice of dietary supplements for improving bone health. While calcium is crucial, taking it alone may not enough. To actually get calcium into your bones, the body relies on other