(44, 'pqq-60', 6, 'PQQ ', 'New vitamin supercharges the brain', 'Helps improve memory, concentration, attention, information identification, recall and processing ability.', '<p>PQQ (pyrroloquinoline quinone) is a type of B vitamin with potent antioxidant and anti-inflammatory properties, effectively protecting nerve cells from damage and death.</p>\n<h5>Key Benefits:</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Helps improve memory and concentration</li>\n<li>Bio PQQ is manufactured using a patented natural fermentation process to enhance absorption</li>\n<li>It is 100% derived from naturally sourced materials</li>\n<li>Bio PQQ is non synthetic</li>\n<li>Bio PQQ is the only PPQ that is clinically proven</li>\n<li>Provides additional cognitive support if use is combined with CoQ10 (INNO-Q-NOL UltraSorb)</li>\n</ul>', '<p>PQQ (pyrroloquinoline quinone) is a type of B vitamin, essential for overall health.&nbsp;&nbsp;PQQ may have potent antioxidant and&nbsp;&nbsp;anti-inflammatory properties, effectively protecting nerve cells from damage and death.</p>\n<p>PQQ also enhances the biosynthesis of nerve growth factor (NGF), a key protein involved in the growth and survival of nerve cells.</p>\n<p>PQQ activates genes that govern mitochondrial reproduction, protection, and repair in the brain. &nbsp;Essentially PQQ enhances the biosynthesis of mitochondria (the powerhouse of a cell).&nbsp;</p>', '<div><span class=\\"bold\\">Medicinal Ingredients: </span>Each vegetarian capsule contains:</div>\n<div>Pyrroloquinoline quinone (disodium salt) as BioPQQTM &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;..10 mg</div>\n<div>&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<div><span class=\\"bold\\">Non-medicinal Ingredients</span>: Hypromellose (vegetarian capsule), colloidal silicon</div>\n<div>\n<div>dioxide, microcrystalline cellulose, magnesium stearate.</div>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div>Free from wheat, gluten, dairy, corn, eggs, soy, nuts, peanuts, fish, shellfish, yeast,</div>\n<div>\n<div>sugar, GMO, artificial colours, flavours</div>\n<div>and preservatives.</div>\n<div>QUALITY, PURITY AND POTENCY GUARANTEED.</div>\n</div>\n<div>BioPQQTM is a registered trademark of MGC, Inc.</div>', '<div><span class=\\"bold\\">Directions for Use:</span> Adults (19 years and over): Take 1 capsule twice daily, or as</div>\n<div>\n<div>directed by a healthcare practitioner. For better results, use in combination with</div>\n</div>\n<div>Inno-Q-Nol&reg; UltraSorb&reg;.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><span class=\\"bold\\">Warnings</span>: Consult a healthcare practitioner prior to use if you are pregnant or</div>\n<div>\n<div>breastfeeding.</div>\n</div>\n<div><span class=\\"bold\\">Cautions</span>: Do not use if the seal is broken. Keep out of reach of children. Store in a</div>\n<div>\n<div>cool dry place to preserve freshness.</div>\n</div>', '', '', 'PQQ', '', '', '', '<p>La PQQ (pyrroloquinol&eacute;ine quinone) est un type de vitamine B essentiel &agrave; la sant&eacute; en g&eacute;n&eacute;ral. La PQQ s\\''est av&eacute;r&eacute;e pouvoir am&eacute;liorer divers aspects cruciaux au fonctionnement mental, incluant l\\''attention, l\\''identification de l\\''information, l\\''habilit&eacute; &agrave; traiter l\\''information, la m&eacute;moire &agrave; court terme et la relation spatiale. La PQQ d\\''Innovite Health est obtenue par un proc&eacute;d&eacute; naturel de fermentation brevet&eacute; pour en am&eacute;liorer son absorption. Elle est d&eacute;riv&eacute;e &agrave; 100% de mati&egrave;res premi&egrave;res de source naturelle. Chaque capsule v&eacute;g&eacute;tarienne contient 10 mg de pyrroloquinol&eacute;ine quinone (disodique) sous forme de BIoPQQ<sup>MC</sup>.</p>', '', '', '', '', 0, 'Yes', '', '80047056', 'Active');
