(51, 'sb10240', 4, 'Fast Joint Relief', 'Pain-free joints in less than 5 days', 'Supports healthy joints and connective tissue.', '<p>Fast Joint Relief is formulated with Apr&egrave;sFLEX&reg;,the next generation extract of Boswellia serratea and new patent-pending therapeutic ingredient that targets and manages the biological and chemical mechanisms responsible for inflammation, thereby providing improvement in overall comfort and flexibility.&nbsp;</p>\n<h5 class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\"><span class=\\"tx-largebold bold\\"><strong>Key Benefits:</strong></span><span class=\\"bold\\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Helps relieve joint pain in as little as 5 days</li>\n<li>Promotes healthy joints, connective tissues and respiratory and digestive function</li>\n<li>Helps protect against further collagen degradation, which will help stop the deterioration of join and connective tissue</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\\"MsoNoSpacing\\">Use Fast Joint Relief before or in combination with the joint rebuilder <strong>Joint Restore.</strong></p>', '<p>Fast Joint Relief helps relieve joint pain in as little as 5 days while also helping to prevent further joint deterioration.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The active ingredient in Fast Joint Relief is Apr&egrave;sFLEX&reg;, a new,</p>\n<p>patent-pending therapeutic ingredient targeting mediators of comfort and</p>\n<p>flexibility (5-lipoxygenase, 5-LOX activating protein (FLAP),</p>\n<p>TNF- and other important mechanisms). &nbsp;By supporting normal, healthy</p>\n<p>levels of these mediators, Apr&egrave;sFLEX&reg; promotes healthy joints, connective</p>\n<p>tissues and respiratory and digestive function. In a recent clinical study,</p>\n<p>Apr&egrave;sFLEX&reg; supplementation demonstrated significant improvements in</p>\n<p>joint comfort, function and mobility&mdash;all within as little as 5 days! Several</p>\n<p>objective blood markers of systemic activity were significantly improved as well.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Apr&egrave;sFLEX&reg; is the next generation extract of Boswellia serrate,</p>\n<p>standardized to 30% acetyl-11-keto-&szlig;-boswellic acid (AKBA). &nbsp;When combined with the</p>\n<p>other inflammation support ingredients, &nbsp;the</p>\n<p>synergism exceeds the expected benefit of the individual ingredients. When</p>\n<p>compared to the leading Boswellia extract on the market, the unique</p>\n<p>composition of Apr&egrave;sFLEX&reg; demonstrated:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>higher and faster absorption of AKBA</li>\n<li>greater bioactivity on 5-LOX inhibition</li>\n<li>more effectively inhibited MMP-3 activity</li>\n<li>faster therapeutic response</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Inhibiting 5-LOX and MMP-3 means Apr&egrave;sFLEX&reg; can help protect against</p>\n<p>further collagen degradation, which will help stop the deterioration of joint</p>\n<p>and connective tissue.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Use Fast Joint Relief before or in combination with the joint rebuilder&nbsp;<strong>Joint Restore.</strong></p>', '<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><span class=\\"bold\\">Medicinal Ingredients:</span> Each vegetarian capsule contains:</div>\n<div>Apres Flex&reg; (Boswellia serrata extract, std to 30% AKBA).&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.100 mg</div>\n<div>\n<div>Vitamin C (ascorbic acid).&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;...10 mg</div>\n<div><span class=\\"bold\\">Non-medicinal Ingredients</span>: Hypromellose (vegetarian capsule), colloidal silicon</div>\n</div>\n<div>dioxide, microcrystalline cellulose, magnesium stearate.</div>\n<div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<span class=\\"bold\\">QUALITY, PURITY AND POTENCY GUARANTEED.</span></div>\n<div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div>Free from wheat, gluten, dairy,</div>\n<div>eggs, soy, nuts, peanuts, fish,</div>\n<div>\n<div>shellfish, yeast, sugar, artificial</div>\n<div>colours, flavours or preservatives.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div>Apres Flex&reg; is a registered trademark of Laila Nutraceuticals</div>\n<div>\n<div>exclusively licensed to PL Thomas &ndash; Laila Nutra LLC.</div>\n<div>International patents pending.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n</div>', '<div><span class=\\"bold\\">Directions for Use</span>: Adults (19 years and over): Take 1 capsule daily with food,</div>\n<div>or as directed by a healthcare practitioner.</div>\n<div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><span class=\\"bold\\">Warnings</span>: Consult a healthcare practitioner prior to use if you are pregnant or</div>\n</div>\n<div>breastfeeding.</div>\n<div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><span class=\\"bold\\">Cautions:</span> Do not use if the seal is broken. Keep out of reach of children. Store in a</div>\n</div>\n<div>cool dry place to preserve freshness.</div>', '', '', 'Soulagement Rapide Des Articulations', '', '', '', '<p>Innovite Health SOULAGEMENT RAPIDE DES ARTICULATIONS aide &agrave; apaiser la douleur articulaire en aussi peu que 5 jours. Aide &eacute;galement &agrave; pr&eacute;venir une plus grande d&eacute;t&eacute;rioration des articulations.</p>', '<p>Cynatine FLX (solubilized keratin)|500 mg Vitamin C (ascorbic acid)|10 mg</p>', '', '', '', 1, 'Yes', '', '519889', 'Active'),
(52, 'sb10242', 4, 'Joint Restore', 'Reduce inflammation, build joint resiliency and improve mobility', 'Helps build and strengthen joint cartilage', '<p>Joint Restore&reg; provides nutritional support for long-term healthy joint structure and function. Formulation utilizes Cynatine&reg; FLX, revolutionary joint care ingredient comprised of a naturally occuring, fibrous solubilized protein, keratin, key for buildling structural components within the body. &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n<p><span class=\\"bold\\">Key Benefits</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\\"bold\\">Supplies joint building blocks:&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;Provides the essential bioactive high sulfur precursors that cells use to rebuild vital joint tissue - faster</li>\n<li><span class=\\"bold\\">Reduces inflammation: </span>Suppresses&nbsp;inflammatory and pain receptors &nbsp;associated with joint degradation.</li>\n<li><span class=\\"bold\\">Improves mobility and b</span><span style=\\"font-weight: bold;\\">uilds joint resiliency:&nbsp;</span>Activates potent enzymatic antioxidants in the body</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Joint Restore&reg; provides nutritional support for long-term healthy joint structure and function. Formulation utilizes Cynatine&reg; FLX which works in 4 ways:</p>\n<p><br /><strong>CYNATINE&reg; FLX BUILDS JOINT RESILIENCE</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Cynatine&reg; FLX supplies the key building blocks for joint repair. It provides the essential bioactive high sulfur precursors that cells use to rebuild vital joint tissue, faster.</li>\n<li>The only joint mobility product that contains the building blocks needed for joint repair and remodeling of tissue.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br /><strong>CYNATINE&reg; FLX HELPS REDUCE INFLAMMATION</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Cynatine&reg; FLX suppresses the inflammatory mediators associated with degradation of the joint. Without the anti-inflammatory properties of Cynatine&reg; FLX, long term inflammation can lead to further erosion and assault on the joint.</li>\n<li>Reduced inflammation means reduced pain and more activity.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br /><strong>&nbsp;CYNATINE&reg; FLX IMPROVES MOBILITY</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Cynatine&reg; FLX activates highly potent enzymatic antioxidants in the body. Unlike most antioxidants that require one molecule of antioxidant to be sacrificed for every free radical, one molecule of enzymatic antioxidants can quench millions of free radicals.</li>\n<li>Cynatine&reg; FLX is a \\''Force Multiplier for the Body\\''s Natural Defence\\'' by increasing the production of superoxide dismutase (SOD) and glutathione.</li>\n<li>An important aspect of Cynatine&reg; FLX potent antioxidant activity is the promotion of glutathione production, a major antioxidant present in all parts of the body.</li>\n<li>Research data indicates that ingested Cynatine&reg; FLX helps to build the cells\\'' glutathione supply, resulting in an increase in glutathione-dependent peroxidase (GSH-PX), which is a primary defense against oxidative damage.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br /><strong>CYNATINE&reg; FLX PROTECTS THE JOINT</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Cynatine&reg; FLX has intrinsic natural antioxidant activity. Even when it is not involved in rallying the body\\''s own defenses, Cynatine&reg; FLX is still exerting a potent antioxidant affect.</li>\n<li>By increasing antioxidant defenses, Cynatine&reg; FLX can reduce the damage in joints caused by free radicals, which cause oxidative stress. This suppresses the inflammatory response which ultimately results in pain reduction and increased mobility.&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>', '<h2>\n<p style=\\"font-size: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\"><span class=\\"bold\\">Medicinal Ingredients: </span>Each capsule contains:</p>\n<p style=\\"font-size: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\">Cynatine&reg; FLX (solubilized keratin) &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.................................................... 500 mg</p>\n<p style=\\"font-size: 10px; font-weight: normal;\\">Vitamin C (ascorbic acid) &