(1, 'Cardiovascular | atherosclerosis | hypertension | stroke | heart attack', 'Cardiovascular Health', 'Includes support for: heart, blood vessels, circulation, cholesterol levels and blood pressure.', '<h2>Your heart works hard all day, every day.</h2>\n<h4><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">It&rsquo;s your most #MostDevotedBodyPart. Show it you care.</span></h4>\n<p><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">For over 30 years Innovite Health has been inspiring wellness and developing ways to nourish and repair our bodies.&nbsp; We believe that when the body&rsquo;s core systems, like &nbsp;cardiovascular, work properly optimal health can be achieved.&nbsp; </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">Our family of heart health products help create that synergistic balance with a strong nutritional foundation that addresses the body&rsquo;s depleted reserves. &nbsp;The goal is to nourish and rebuild the body from the inside out.&nbsp; By restoring nutrients and repairing damage, you can reclaim your health.</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">This year, heart disease will affect more women in Canada than any other disease.&nbsp; Let us show you how to take care of your #MostDevotedBodyPart.&nbsp; Our full spectrum heart care line includes support for: heart, blood vessels, circulation, cholesterol levels and blood pressure.&nbsp; </span></p>', 'Santé cardiovasculaire', 'aa', 'Includes support for: heart, blood vessels, circulation, cholesterol levels and blood pressure.', '<p>xx</p>', 'Heart disease affects more women in Canada than any other disease.   Innovite Health supports: heart, blood vessels, circulation, cholesterol and blood pressure.   Inno-Q-Nol  is #1 CoQ10.', 'Cardiovascular Health', 1, '8JevFuSuay.jpg'),
(2, 'Detox and Yeast Buster | anti-microbial | anti-fungal | anti-microbial | GI', 'Detox and Yeast Buster®', 'Includes support for: probiotics, candida and general detox.', '<h2><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">Restore internal purity and balance </span></h2>\n<h3><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">Natural, safe and effective cleansing</span></h3>\n<p><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">Toxins build up in your body &ndash; that is the reality of 21<sup>st</sup> century living.&nbsp; Support a total body detox by letting Innovite help nourish and rebuild the body from the inside out, thus achieving optimal health.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">The human body is an inherent self-cleaning organism.&nbsp; Without the elaborate and multi-organ system of detoxification, we would not survive. However, sometime we do need help in improving our eliminatory functions. Avoid headaches, fatigue, weight gain and microbials.&nbsp; </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">Yeast Buster candida detox has been a leading treatment for over 25 successful years.&nbsp; The new improved formula now includes Licorice in Activated Charcoal for even easier digestion.&nbsp; Try it and get back on track to healthy living.</span></p>', 'Detox and Yeast Buster', 'Detox and Digestive Restoration', 'Includes support for: probiotics, candida and general detox.', '<p>Today everyone is exposed to synthetic, often toxic chemicals on an unprecedented scale. Industrial chemicals and their pollutants run-off in our water, pesticides, additives in our foods, heavy metals, anesthetics, residues from drugs and environmental pollutants, are all trapped within the human body in greater concentration. Every system of the body is affected, from tissue damage to sensory deterioration. This doesn&rsquo;t include second-hand smoke, caffeine and alcohol overload or daily stress, that are an increasing part of our lives. Any form of over indulgence, be it new year&rsquo;s eve parties, Thanksgiving, stag parties or weekend getaways, will build up toxins in our bodies. As toxic matter saturates our tissues, antioxidants and minerals in vital body fluids are reduced and immune defenses are thrown out of balance.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>A surplus of these toxic substances can encourage the formation of cellulite or fatty deposits and provoke an unhealthy complexion. It is therefore not surprising that from time to time, especially at the end of all seasons, we feel heavy, lethargic and sluggish.</p>\n<p>One of the best ways to remain healthy in a destructive environment is having a body cleanse. Almost everyone can benefit from a body cleanse. Cleanse programs help to relieve common digestive disorders and chronic persistent symptoms, by promoting the elimination of accumulated toxins in the body.</p>', 'All natural cleanse, purify and replenishment of healthy bacteria. Innovite Health supplement support includes: general detox and candida detox programs (Yeast Buster)', 'Detox and Yeast Buster', 4, 'AwnruLlYc3.jpg'),
(3, 'Probiotics | Digestive Restoration | IBS | Crohn’s | Colitis | Leaky Gut', 'Probiotics and Digestive Restoration', 'Probiotics are good bacteria that normally reside in the gastrointestinal tract. ', '<h2><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">What&rsquo;s inside counts</span></h2>\n<h3><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">Human sourced probiotics</span></h3>\n<p><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">As a probiotic science and innovation leader, Innovite Health &nbsp;utilizes proprietary &nbsp;strains with decades &nbsp;of proven efficacy and clinical results.&nbsp; Our commitment to incorporate the safest and most effective strains &nbsp;reflect the latest evidence-based research from human trials. Our probiotics are human-sourced strains, proven in human clinical trials and cover a solid range effective for any member of the family.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Probiotiques', 'Probiotic', 'Probiotics are good bacteria that normally reside in the gastrointestinal tract. ', '', 'Human-sourced strain DDS probiotics, proven in human clinical trials and cover a solid range effective for any member of the family. Try Gut Repair for leaky gut syndrome.', 'Human-sourced strain DDS probiotics, proven in human clinical trials and cover a solid range effective for any member of the family. Try Gut Repair for leaky gut syndrome.', 5, '6RZ098eujU.jpg'),
(4, 'Muscular Skeletal | natural | osteoporosis | fibromyalgia | arthritis', 'Muscular Skeletal Therapies', 'Includes support for: bone, joint, connective tissue, muscle and skin health.', '<h2><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">Strong.&nbsp; Stronger.&nbsp; Strongest.</span></h2>\n<h3><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">Stretch your flexibility and build bone strength</span><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></h3>\n<p><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">You stand tall, head held high. &nbsp;Being aware of your body&rsquo;s needs and nurturing it, you are committed to protecting the gifts you have been given.&nbsp; You are strong and resilient like a tree, bending and swaying gracefully under pressure but standing tall knowing your foundation is solid.&nbsp; <br /></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">Innovite Health believes that a strong core begins with a strong nutritional foundation, helping to restore nutrients, repair the body and reclaim your health. &nbsp;Ground-breaking natural ingredients, combined with the latest scientific research and clinical evidence is used to create the most natural and effective formulas to optimize your health.&nbsp; Battle hard against the general wear and tear on your body.&nbsp; Help in the fight against muscular skeletal afflictions like osteoporosis. &nbsp;&nbsp;Our muscular skeletal therapies includes support for: bone, joint, connective tissue, muscle and skin health.</span></p>', 'Santé des os et des articulations', 'Muscular Skeletal Therapies', 'Includes support for: bone, joint, connective tissue, muscle and skin health.', '<p>While significant studies have been made in understanding bone and joint health and disease over the last few decades, most people do not pay enough attention to proactively managing their bone and joint health.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Innovite Health offers a wide range of products to promote bone and joint health.</p>', 'Improve mobility and flexibility with Innovite Health supplement support: bone, joint, connective tissue, muscle and skin health. Be pain-free in 5 days with Fast Joint Relief.', 'Improve mobility and flexibility with Innovite Health supplement support: bone, joint, connective tissue, muscle and skin health. Be pain-free in 5 days with Fast Joint Relief.', 3, 'cjjbGyDOCG.jpg'),
(5, 'Anti-aging | Vision | Menopause | PMS | metabolism | stress', 'Anti-aging Care', 'Includes support for: female health and vision care.', '<h2><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">Purify, rejuvenate and energize</span></h2>\n<h3><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">Look young, act young, feel young</span></h3>\n<p><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">Consuming the right nutrients can keep you healthy and balanced &ndash; especially&nbsp; as you age.&nbsp; Keeping your metabolism upbeat, reducing the stresses associated with menopause and ensuring vision care are top notch are just some of the priorities we are focussed on here at Innovite Health.&nbsp; &nbsp;We have been inspiring wellness for over 30 years and developing ways to nourish and repair our bodies. We believe that when the body&rsquo;s core systems work in synergy, optimal health can be achieved.</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">That synergistic balance relies on a strong nutritional foundation. With today&rsquo;s lifestyle, many factors contribute to depleting the body&rsquo;s reserves of these critical nutrients. Our goal at Innovite Health is to nourish and heal the body from the inside out. By restoring nutrients and repairing damage, you can reclaim your health.</span></p>', 'Style de vie saine', 'Anti-aging Care', 'Includes support for: female health and vision care.', '<p>Herbal supplements are more popular now than ever before. People are looking for new ways to improve their health, and they are turning to natural remedies rather than pharmaceutical drugs more and more.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>As such, there have been countless studies performed on the therapeutic benefits and applications of various herbs and herbal extracts. Much of this research presents strong evidence that taking herbal supplements in conjunction with a healthy diet and lifestyle can be beneficial.&nbsp;</p>', 'Increase energy, curb menopause symptoms and maintain strong vision with Innovite Health all-natural supplements. Try Total Iron to beat fatigue.', 'Increase energy, curb menopause symptoms and maintain strong vision with Innovite Health all-natural supplements. Try Total Iron to beat fatigue.', 6, '2Wgtiu18nT.jpg'),
(6, 'Cognitive and Mood | Alzheimer’s | autism | Parkinson’s', 'Mood and Cognitive Support', 'Includes support for: memory, nerves, stress, sleep and mood enhancement.', '<h2><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">Supercharge your brain</span></h2>\n<h3><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">Improve overall IQ performance</span></h3>\n<p><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">Innovite Health has been leading the charge to inspire health and wellness.&nbsp; We develop ways to nourish and rebuild the body from the inside out, thus achieving optimal health.</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\\"EN-CA\\">Our family of mood and cognitive health products addresses the growing need to ensure that our brains and nervous systems are in top notch condition.&nbsp; From sharpening your memory, improving the nervous system, calming nerves and sleep and mood enhancement, Innovite Health leads the way to supercharge your brain.</span></p>', 'SANTÉ DU CERVEAU', 'Mood and Cognitive Support', 'Includes support for: memory, nerves, stress, sleep and mood enhancement.', '<p>Most Canadians (78%) think brain health is at least as important as physical health - but aren\\''t sure what it takes to keep their brain in good shape. The benefits of taking a preventative approach in early ages still haven&rsquo;t hit home with most people, but their fears of Alzheimer&rsquo;s, dementia, and everyday memory loss are growing by leaps and bounds. Alzheimer\\''s disease affects an estimated 1 in 10 people over age 65. As many as 10 million baby boomers are expected to develop Alzheimer&rsquo;s.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Innovite Health intends to lead the way to help Canadians to improve their brain health. We have developed a whole range of products to help reduce risks and improve conditions of the brain disease.</p>', 'Neurological disorder support with Innovite Health: memory, concentration, nervous system, sleep and mood. PQQ and CoQ10 can supercharge your brain.', 'Neurological disorder support with Innovite Health: memory, concentration, nervous system, sleep and mood. PQQ and CoQ10 can supercharge your brain.', 2, 'YlRBHRV7DY.jpg');
