(7, 5, 'I\\''m on the Yeast Buster Candida program and I\\''m loving it. Day 11 today and am feeling a huge difference already in my energy level.\n', 4.0, '', 'Christine M. ', 'shark74@rogers.com', '2014-01-28 14:04:03', 'Yes', 'Active'),
(8, 5, 'I\\''ve been using the yeast buster kit for about 2 weeks now, I plan on using it for about a month at least. Let me just start by saying, you guys have a phenomenal product! The die off symptoms are very strong, but it\\''s amazing how quick your health can turn the corner. Candida has destroyed my quality of life, but I can feel my system regulating itself day by day.\n', 5.0, '', 'Danny B.', 'dannyburns88@hotmail.com', '2014-01-28 14:05:19', 'Yes', 'Active'),
(9, 27, 'I am 71 years old and since 1984 my optometrist told me I had the start of glaucoma. In 1986 we moved to Courtenay, B.C. Vancouver Island, saw an optometrist here and again the same answer, I was not surprised because my father had glaucoma. Every year I had a check-up, then a number of years ago my optometrist sent me to a ophthalmologist here, again I would see him every year. Then about four years ago I saw in the health food store your product Inno-Vision.  I bought the product, took it 3 times a day and four months later I had an appointment with the eye specialist and he surprised me with his answer “NO SIGN OF GLAUCOMA’ you can image how happy I was. Recently had an appointment again and again no sign of glaucoma. Four years ago I bought your product, four years of no sign of glaucoma I decided to write to you how your product works if a person has glaucoma. I will take it forever. I would like to know what product I could take for cataract, start of cataract, I don’t seem to have any problems yet, have an appointment in 6 months time, as long as I don’t have a problem he won’t operate, so what can I take beside inno-vision and not to have cataract surgery.  Thank you.', 5.0, '', 'Betsy K-B.', 'betsiekb@xplornet.com', '2014-01-28 14:07:00', 'Yes', 'Active'),
(10, 21, 'My  aunt-in-law, who had osteoporosis for many years,is unable to tolerate bisphosphonates (like many people) and no longer getting them. She is now on this product and her last bone density scan has improved.  So thank you!\n', 1.0, '', 'Anonymous', 'test@test.com', '2014-01-29 17:42:57', 'Yes', 'Active'),
(11, 19, 'Both my wife and I take this product. My wife finds that it helps minimize her irregular heartbeat. \n', 5.0, '', 'Herb V.', 'herboranne@yahoo.ca', '2014-01-29 17:45:09', 'Yes', 'Active'),
(12, 19, 'I am already feeling much better. Its amazing that the effect is almost immediate. I had a tightness in the chest area for a long time and within a few days I have already felt a big difference. I am breathing better too.', 5.0, '', 'Suzette L.', 'suzette_lefebvre@hc-sc.gc.ca', '2014-01-29 17:46:36', 'Yes', 'Active'),
(13, 19, 'INNO-Q-NOL is truly helping my condition [Parkinson\\''s] and I hope one day that testing/research will commence\n', 5.0, '', 'Robekah C.', 'robekahk@shaw.ca', '2014-01-29 17:48:29', 'Yes', 'Active');
