(71, 1, '2011-02-25 13:05:18', '2011-02-25 13:05:18', 'Grapefruit seed extract is made from the seeds of the grapefruit and is used for its antibacterial, antiseptic and purifying properties. Grapefruit seed extract clears the body of harmful bacteria, viruses, infection and fungi, simultaneously promoting and protecting the immune system. It has the ability to rid the body of some parasites as well.\r\n\r\nGrapefruit seed extract has an alkalizing effect on the body and is considered one the strongest foods for promoting alkaline in the body. For optimum health, alkaline and acid levels must be balanced in the body, which is referred as the pH level. Excess acids create oxidation, effectively causing the body to decay and become sick.\r\n\r\nThe powerful antibacterial, antifungal and antimicrobial properties of grapefruit seed extract make it useful in fighting a large range of infections, parasites and viruses. It can be used both internally and externally to treat gastrointestinal and digestive upsets, infections and viruses of any kind, including the flu, tooth and gum infections, ear and throat infections, sinusitis, chronic fatigue, parasite infections and much more.\r\n<h3>Grapefruit seed extract is a multipurpose product with countless applications<strong>.</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wound Healing<strong> — </strong>Good for fast healing of scar tissue associated with many types of wounds.</li>\r\n	<li>Household Uses — Vegetable wash, counter tops, cutting boards, laundry cleaner, etc.</li>\r\n	<li>Travel Uses — Grapefruit extract is used against water and food borne illnesses, diarrhea, dysentery, etc.</li>\r\n	<li>Gardening Uses — Tool cleaner to remove fungus, mold. As a bug spray, plant spray and more!</li>\r\n	<li>Pet Health — Internal and external conditions and infections, skin conditions, mange, fleas, etc.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Grapefruit Seed Extract - Frontline Defense against Germs', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'grapefruit-seed-extract-frontline-defense-against-germs', '', '', '2011-02-25 13:08:20', '2011-02-25 13:08:20', '', 0, 'http://www.inno-vite.com/articles/?p=71', 0, 'post', '', 0),
