(127, 1, '2011-02-25 13:35:47', '2011-02-25 13:35:47', '<div>\r\n\r\nFeeling sluggish or out of sync? Having skin problems, aches and pains, or digestive problems? Straying from your healthier habits lately? It might be time for a detox.\r\n\r\nIn this day and age we are all exposed to thousands of toxins, chemicals, and parasites through the air we breathe, through the food and water supply, and through the use of pharmaceutical drugs. We are also eating more sugar and processed foods than ever before, and abuse our bodies on a regular basis with various sedatives, painkillers and stimulants.\r\n\r\nScientists have studied the levels of toxins in the human body, and their findings are very disturbing. Research proves that our bodies are not capable of eliminating the multitude of toxins and chemicals we inhale and ingest on a daily basis. These toxins accumulate in our cells, blood, tissues, organs, and the build up of all of this toxic internal waste may cause serious health problems.\r\n\r\nBelow is a list of some of the symptoms that you may experience if you are due for a cleanse.\r\n\r\n•    Frequent fatigue\r\n•    Low energy\r\n•    Flatulence, gas &amp; bloating\r\n•    Excess weight\r\n•    Food allergies\r\n•    Impaired digestion\r\n•    Irritability, mood swings\r\n•    Bad breath &amp; foul-smelling stools\r\n•    Parasites in stool\r\n•    Frequent colds\r\n•    Recurring headaches\r\n•    Chronic constipation\r\n•    Irritable bowel syndrome (IBS)\r\n•    Protruding belly (“pooch”)\r\n•    Powerful food cravings\r\n•    Skin problems, rashes, acne etc.\r\n•    Metallic taste in mouth\r\n•    Chronic diarrhea\r\n•    Mental fog\r\n•    Inflamed joints\r\n\r\nWhether you went a little crazy over the holidays, or are simply trying to jump start a new diet regimen, there are specific foods that you can eat to help detoxify your system. You should aim for foods that are high in fiber and/or vitamin C as they’re great antioxidants for the body.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Time to Detox ?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'time-to-detox', '', '', '2011-02-25 13:37:31', '2011-02-25 13:37:31', '', 0, 'http://www.inno-vite.com/articles/?p=127', 0, 'post', '', 0),
