(518, 1, '2012-08-23 20:07:15', '2012-08-23 20:07:15', 'Coenzyme Q10 (CoQ10) is an extremely important nutrient that every cell in your body must have in order to produce energy. The heart has a huge demand for CoQ10; therefore, CoQ10 deficiency can trigger or worsen some serious cardiovascular problems such as angina, cardiomyopathy and high blood pressure.\r\n\r\nOne of the most remarkable studies on CoQ10 involved the significant improvement of individuals expected to die of heart failure. When these patients were supplemented with CoQ10, this miracle nutrient astounded physicians by improving blood pumping capabilities and reducing heart size, surpassing researcher’s expectations.\r\n\r\nSince this study many more clinical trials have been conducted to unveil CoQ10’s immense value in treating heart patients. CoQ10 has also been shown to be effective in reducing mild to moderate hypertension, as well as counteracting the serious adverse effects of cholesterol-lowering medications called statins.', 'CoQ10 – The wonder ingredient to protect your heart!', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '501-revision-2', '', '', '2012-08-23 20:07:15', '2012-08-23 20:07:15', '', 501, 'http://www.inno-vite.com/articles/501-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
